quran[842]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Ngalabo abahlelwe ngezigaba
  37,2,Ngalabo abahambisa amafu ngendlela enhle
  37,3,Ngalabo abafunda isikhumbuzo
  37,4,Ngempela uMvelinqangi wenu munye
  37,5,INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nako konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili neNkosi yempumalanga
  37,6,Ngempela thina salihlobisa izulu eliseduzane ngomhlobiso wezinkanyezi
  37,7,"Nokulondolozwa\tkwalo\tmayelana\tnabobonke\tosathane abahlubukayo"
  37,8,Abakwazi ukulalela inhlangano ephakeme kakhulu futhi bajikijelwa kuwona wonke amacala
  37,9,Bayaxoshwa futhi okwabo yisijeziso sangunaphakade
  37,10,Ngaphandle kwalowo ohlwitha okuthize ngokuntshontsha bese elandelwa yilangabi lomlilo elihlabayo
  37,11,Ngakho-ke babuze ukuthi ngakube yibona yini abanzima ekudaleni noma yilabo esabadalayo na? Ngempela thina sabadala ngobumba olunamathelayo
  37,12,Kepha uyamangala kulapho benza inhlekisa
  37,13,Futhi uma bekhunjuziswa abakhumbuli
  37,14,Futhi uma bebona uphawu benza inhlekisa
  37,15,"Futhi\tbathi,\t“lokhu\takuyilutho\tngaphandle\tkomlingo ogqamile”"
  37,16,Ngakube uma sesifile saphenduka uthuli namathambo ngempela siyovuswa yini na
  37,17,Kanye nobaba bethu basendulo na
  37,18,"Ithi, “yebo futhi nina niyothotshiswa"
  37,19,Kuyoba ukukhala okukodwa kuphela kulapho bona bebhekile
  37,20,"Futhi bayothi, “Oh usizi kuthina! lolu wusuku lwenhlawulo”"
  37,21,Lolu wusuku lokugcina enaniluphika
  37,22,Baqoqeleni ndawonye labo ababeyizoni kanye namaqembu abo kanye nakho konke loko ababekukhonza
  37,23,Esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bese nibaholela endleleni yesihogo
  37,24,Futhi nibamise ngempela ukuze babuzwe
  37,25,Kwenzenjani ngani nangalekelelani na
  37,26,Kepha bona ngalolosuku bayozinikela
  37,27,Futhi abanye babo bayophendukela kwabanye bebuzana bodwa
  37,28,"Bayothi,\t“ngempela\tnina\tnaniza\tkuthina\tniqhamuka ngakwesokudla”"
  37,29,"Bayothi, “kepha naningeyiwona amakholwa”"
  37,30,"Futhi sasingenalo igunya phezulu kwenu, kepha nina naningabantu abephula umthetho"
  37,31,Ngakho-ke liyaqiniseka kuthina izwi leNkosi yethu ngempela thina sizozwa
  37,32,Manjalo saniphambukisa (endleleni eqondile) ngempela nathi sasiphambukile
  37,33,Ngakho-ke ngempela bona ngalolosuku bazoba ngababelanayo esijezisweni
  37,34,Ngempela sibenza kanjalo abayizoni
  37,35,"Ngempela bona kwakuthi uma kuthiwa kubona, “ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi” bese bayaziqhayisa"
  37,36,"Futhi bathi, “ngakube thina sizoyeka onkulunkulu bethu ngenxa yembongi ehlanyayo na"
  37,37,Kepha ulethe iqiniso futhi uqinisekisa izithunywa
  37,38,Ngempela nina nizosizwa isijeziso esibuhlungu
  37,39,Futhi angeke ninikezwe umvuzo ngaphandle kwalokho enanikwenza
  37,40,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zikaMvelinqangi ezimsulwa
  37,41,Labo-ke okwabo yisabelo esaziwayo
  37,42,"Izithelo, futhi bona bangabahlonishwa"
  37,43,Ezivandeni zenjabulo
  37,44,Ezihlalweni zobukhosi bebhekene
  37,45,Siyozungeleziswa kubona isitsha esinewayini
  37,46,"Elimhlophe, elimtoti kwabaliphuzayo"
  37,47,Abukho ubungozi kulona futhi bona abakutholi ukudakwa kulona
  37,48,"Futhi\teduzane\tnabo\tkuyoba\tnabesifazane\tabamsulwa abanamehlo amahle"
  37,49,Okusengathi bona abesifazane bangamaqanda angakaze athintwe
  37,50,Ngakho-ke abanye babo bayophendukela kwabanye bebuzana
  37,51,"Isikhulumi\tphakathi\tkwabo\tsiyothi,\t“ngempela\tmina nganginomngane”"
  37,52,"Owayethi,\t“ngakube\tngempela\twena\tungomunye wabakholwayo na"
  37,53,Ngakube uma sesifile sabawuthuli namathambo ngakube ngempela siyojeziswa”
  37,54,"Wathi, “Singaya yini ukuyobabona?”"
  37,55,Ngakho-ke wabheka phansi wambona esesihogweni
  37,56,"Wathi, “ngoMvelinqangi! Ucishe wangenza ngabhubha”"
  37,57,"Futhi\tukube\tbekungesingenxa\tyomusa\tweNkosi\tyami ngempela bengizokuba ngomunye wabalethiwe"
  37,58,Ngakube thina angeke sife
  37,59,Ngaphandle kokufa kwethu kwasekuqaleni futhi ngakube angeke yini sibe ngabajeziswayo na
  37,60,Ngempela lokhu kungukuphumelela okukhulu
  37,61,Okufana nalokhu ziyakusebenzela izisebenzi
  37,62,Ngakube lokhu kungukujabula okungcono noma yisihlahla sezaQum na
  37,63,Ngempela sasenza saba yisivivinyo kwabayizoni
  37,64,Ngempela sona siphuma esiqwini sesihogo
  37,65,Izithelo zaso zinjengamakhanda osathane
  37,66,Ngakho-ke ngempela bona bayodla kusona bagcwalise izisu ngaso
  37,67,Besekuthi ngempela okwabo phezulu kwaso kube ngamanzi abilayo
  37,68,Besekuthi ngempela ukuphindela kwabo kube semlilweni ovuthayo wesihogo
  37,69,Ngempela bona bathola oyise bedukile
  37,70,Ngakho-ke bona bashesha ezinyathelweni zabo
  37,71,"Futhi\tngempela\tngaphambilini\tkwabo\tladuka\tiningi labasendulo"
  37,72,Futhi ngempela sabathumela kubona abaxwayisi
  37,73,Ngakho-ke bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho sababexwayisiwe
  37,74,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zikaMvelinqangi ezimsulwa
  37,75,"Futhi ngempela uNowa wasibiza, singabaphenduli abangcono kakhulu"
  37,76,Futhi samsindisa kanye nabantu bakhe ekuhluphekeni okukhulu
  37,77,Futhi sayenza inzalo yakhe yaba ngabasalayo
  37,78,Futhi samshiyela (udumo) ezizukulwaneni ezilandelayo
  37,79,Ukuthula makube kuNowa emihlabeni
  37,80,Ngempela sibanika kanjalo umvuzo abenzi bokuhle
  37,81,Ngempela yena ungomunye wezinceku zethu ezikholwayo
  37,82,Sabe sesiyabaminzisa abanye
  37,83,Futhi ngempela eqenjini lakhe kwakukhona u-Abrahamu
  37,84,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\teza\teNkosini\tyakhe\tngenhliziyo ephelele"
  37,85,"Khumbula ngenkathi ethi kuyise nakubantu bakhe, “yini eniyikhonzayo na”"
  37,86,"Ngakube\tngamanga\tizithixo\tenizifisayo\tesikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi na"
  37,87,Ngakube yimuphi umcabango wenu ngeNkosi yemihlaba na
  37,88,Ngakho-ke wajeqeza izinkanyezi kanye
  37,89,"Wayesethi, “ngempela mina ngiyagula”"
  37,90,Ngakho-ke bamfulathela bahamba
  37,91,"Ngakho-ke\twaphendukela\tezithixweni\tzabo\twayesethi, “Ngakube anidli yini na"
  37,92,Kungani ningakhulumi na
  37,93,"Ngakho-ke\twaphendukela\tphezulu\tkwazo,\twazishaya ngesandla sokunene"
  37,94,Manjalo beza kuyena beshesha
  37,95,"Wathi, “Ngakube nikhonza loko enikuqophayo na"
  37,96,Kulapho uMvelinqangi anidala kanye nalokho enikwenzayo
  37,97,"Bathi,\t“makheleni\tisakhiwo\tbese\tnimposa\temlilweni ovuthayo”"
  37,98,Base bemdalela icebo ngakho-ke sabenza babangabehlisiweyo
  37,99,"Futhi wathi, “ngempela mina ngiya eNkosini yami izongihola”"
  37,100,Nkosi yami ngiphe (indodana) kubenzi bokuhle
  37,101,Ngakho-ke samnika izindaba ezinhle zomfana obekezelayo
  37,102,"Manjalo kwathi lapho (indodana yakhe) seyikhule ngokwanele ukuhamba naye wathi, “Oh ndodana yami! Ngempela mina ngibone ephusheni lami\tngikunikela, ngakho-ke bheka ubonani, yathi (indodana yakhe) Oh baba wami! Yenza lokho okuphoqwayo, uzongithola ngingowababekezelayo uma uMvelinqangi ethanda"
  37,103,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho bobabili sebezinikele (entandweni kaMvelinqangi)\tesembeke phansi ngesiphongo"
  37,104,"Sammemeza sathi, “Oh Abrahamu!”"
  37,105,"Ngempela uwufezile umbono, ngempela nathi ngokunjalo sibanika umvuzo abenzi bokuhle"
  37,106,Ngempela lokhu kuwukuvivinywa okucacile
  37,107,Futhi samhlenga ngomnikelo omkhulu
  37,108,Futhi samshiyela (udumo) kwabanye
  37,109,Ukuthula makube ku-Abrahamu
  37,110,Sibanika kanjalo umvuzo abenzi bokuhle
  37,111,Ngempela yena wayengomunye wezinceku zethu ezikholwayo
  37,112,"Futhi samnika izindaba ezinhle zika-Isaka kumphrofethi ongomunye\twabalungileyo"
  37,113,"Futhi sambusisa yena kanye no-Isaka, futhi enzalweni yabo bobabili\tkunabenzi bokuhle kanye nabazona bona uqobo lwabo ngokusobala"
  37,114,Futhi ngempela umusa sawethwesa uMose kanye no-Aroni
  37,115,Futhi sabasindisa bobabili kanye nabantu babo bobabili ekuhluphekeni okukhulu
  37,116,Futhi sabasiza ngakho-ke bona babangabanqobayo
  37,117,Futhi bobabili sabanikeza incwadi ecacile
  37,118,Futhi bobabili sabahola endleleni eqondile
  37,119,"Futhi\tbobabili\tsabashiyela\t(udumo)\tezizukulwaneni zangamumva"
  37,120,Ukuthula makube kuMose naku-Aroni
  37,121,Ngempela sibanika kanjalo umvuzo abenzi bokuhle
  37,122,Ngempela bona bobaili babengabanye bezinceku zethu ezikholwayo
  37,123,Futhi ngempela u-Elyas wayengomunye wezithunywa
  37,124,"Ngenkathi ethi kubantu bakhe, “ngakube animesabi yini (uMvelinqangi) na"
  37,125,Ngakube nimemeza uBali niyeka ongcono kunabo bonke abadali
  37,126,UMvelinqangi yiNkosi yenu neNkosi yoyihlo basendulo
  37,127,Kepha bamphika ngakho-ke ngempela bona bayolethwa ngaphambili
  37,128,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zikaMvelinqangi ezimsulwa
  37,129,Futhi samshiyela (udumo) ezizukulwaneni zangamumva
  37,130,Ukuthula makube ku-Elyas
  37,131,Ngempela sibanika kanjalo umvuzo abenzi bokuhle
  37,132,Ngempela yena wayengomunye wezinceku zethu ezikholwayo
  37,133,Futhi ngempela uLothi wayengomunye wezithunywa
  37,134,Khumbula ngenkathi simsindisa kanye nabantu bakhe bonke
  37,135,"Ngaphandle\tkowesifazane\tomdala\t(unkosikazi\twakhe) owayekanye nabasalele ngemumva"
  37,136,Sabe sesiyababhubhisa abanye
  37,137,Futhi ngempela nina nidlula ngakubona ekuseni
  37,138,"Nasebusuku, ngakube aninawo yini umqondo"
  37,139,Futhi ngempela uYunus (uJona) wayengomunye wezithunywa
  37,140,Khumbula ngenkathi egijima eya emkhunjini ogcwele
  37,141,"Manjalo\twaphonsa\tinkatho\twayeseba\tngomunye wabalahlekelweyo"
  37,142,Ngakho-ke inhlanzi yamgwinya kulapho yena efanelwe ukusolwa
  37,143,Kepha ukuba wayengesiyena omunye wabadumisayo
  37,144,Ngempela wayezohlala esiswini sayo (inhlanzi) kuze kube wusuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo
  37,145,Ngakho-ke samphonsa ogwini olomile kulapho yena egula
  37,146,Futhi samilisa isihlahla soselwa phezulu kwakhe
  37,147,Futhi samthumela kwabayinkulungwane noma ngaphezulu
  37,148,"Ngakho-ke\tbakholwa,\tsabe\tsesibanika\tinjabulo okwesikhashana"
  37,149,Ngakho-ke babuze ngakube okweNkosi yakho ngamadodakazi okwabo ngamadodana na
  37,150,Noma sadala izingelosi zabangabesifazane kulapho bona bebhekile
  37,151,Ngempela kungamanga abo abakushoyo
  37,152,"(Ukuthi)\tUmvelinqangi\twazala\tfuthi\tngempela\tbona banamanga"
  37,153,Wakhetha amadodakazi ngaphezulu kwamadodana na
  37,154,Kwenzekani ngani nehlulela kanjani
  37,155,Lapho-ke ngeke ukhunjuzwe
  37,156,Noma ninegunya elicacile na
  37,157,Ngakho-ke lethani incwadi yenu uma kungukuthi nineqiniso
  37,158,"Futhi benza ubudlelwane phakathi kwakhe namaJinn, futhi ngempela amaJinn azi kahle ukuthi ngempela wona ayolethwa ngaphambili"
  37,159,"Makadunyiswe\tuMvelinqangi\tngaphezulu\tkwalokho abakuchazayo"
  37,160,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zikaMvelinqangi ezimsulwa
  37,161,Ngakho-ke nina kanye nalokho enikukhonzayo
  37,162,Angeke nibalinge ngaye
  37,163,Ngaphandle kwalowo onqunyelwe ukusha esihogweni
  37,164,Futhi akekho namunye wethu ngaphandle kwalowo onendawo eyaziwayo
  37,165,Futhi ngempela thina sime ngolayini
  37,166,Futhi ngempela thina singabadumisayo
  37,167,Futhi babejwayele ukuthi
  37,168,Ukube sasinaso isikhumbuzo esinjengesabantu basendulo
  37,169,Sasizoba yizinceku zikaMvelinqangi eziqotho
  37,170,"Kepha abakholelwanga kusona, ngakho-ke bayokwazi"
  37,171,"Futhi ngempela izwi lethu selahamba ngaphambili laya ezincekwini zethu, izithunywa"
  37,172,Ngempela zona okwazo ukwelekelelwa
  37,173,Futhi ngempela amabutho ethu okwawo ukunqoba
  37,174,Ngakho-ke suka kubona kuze kube yisikhashana
  37,175,Futhi babone ngakho-ke nabo bazobona
  37,176,Ngakube yisijeziso sethu abafuna ukuthi sisheshe
  37,177,Ngakho-ke uma (isijeziso) sesehlela egcekeni labo ngakho-ke kuyokuba kubi ukusa kulabo abaxwayiswayo
  37,178,Ngakho-ke suka kubona kuze kube yisikhashana
  37,179,"Futhi bheka, ngakho-ke nabo bayobona"
  37,180,"Mayidunyiswe iNkosi yakho, iNkosi yamandla ngaphezulu kwalokho abakuchazayo"
  37,181,Futhi ukuthula makube phezulu kwezithunywa
  37,182,Futhi udumo lungolukaMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba
  38,1,"Swad, ngeQur’an enesikhumbuzo"
  38,2,Kepha labo abangakholwanga basekuziphazamiseni nasekuphikisaneni
  38,3,Zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo ngakho-ke zakhala kulapho sasingekho isikhathi sokuphunyuka
  38,4,"Futhi bamangale ukuthi bafikelwe ngumxwayisi ophuma phakathi kwabo futhi abangakholwanga bathi, “lona ngumlubi umqambimanga”"
  38,5,Ngakube wenza izithixo uNkulunkulu oyedwa na? ngempela lokhu kuyinto emangalisayo
  38,6,"Futhi abaholi phakathi kwabo basuka bahamba, hambani futhi nibambelele ezithixweni zenu ngempela lokhu kuyinto ehlosiwe"
  38,7,"Asikaze sizwe ngalokhu enkolweni yokugcina, lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle komqambo"
  38,8,"Ngakube sehliselwe phezulu kwakhe yini isikhumbuzo phakathi kwethu? Kepha bona basekungabazeni mayelana nesikhumbuzo, kepha abakasizwa isijeziso sami"
  38,9,"Noma, ngakube banawo yini amagugu omusa weNkosi yakho ephakeme ngamandla, ephanayo"
  38,10,Nomaokwaboumbusowamazulunomhlabakanyenakokonke okuphakathi kwako kokubili? Ngakho-ke mabakhuphuke ngemizamo (yabo)
  38,11,Isixuku esiyohlulwa lapho phakathi kwezinhlangano
  38,12,Abantu baNowa baphika ngaphambilini kwabo kanye no-Ad noFaro
  38,13,NoThamud nabantu baLothi kanye nezihlali zase-Ayka
  38,14,Babengenzi lutho ngaphandle kokuphika izithunywa ngakho- ke saqiniseka isijeziso sami
  38,15,Futhi laba abalindele lutho ngaphandle kokukhala (kwecilongo) okukodwa angeke kube nokulibala
  38,16,"Futhi bathi, “Nkosi yethu sisheshisele ingxenye yethu ngaphambili kosuku lokubala (lokwahlulela)”"
  38,17,Kubekezelele lokho abakushoyo futhi khumbula inceku yethu uDavide onamandla ngempela yena wayephendukela emumva ngokuzisola
  38,18,Ngempela sazenza izintaba kanye naye ukuthi badumise (uMvelinqangi) kusihlwa nasekuseni
  38,19,"Kanye nezinyoni zaqoqana ndawonye, konke kwakumthobela"
  38,20,Futhi sawuqinisa umbuso wakhe futhi samupha ubuhlakani nokukhuluma
  38,21,Futhi ngakube sezifikile kuwena izindaba zezitha ngenkathi zingena egunjini lokuthandaza na
  38,22,"Ngenkathi zingena kuDavide ngakho-ke wazesaba zathi, “izimbangi ezimbili ungesabi omunye wethu wone omunye ngakho-ke yehlulela phakathi kwethu ngeqiniso futhi ungabi ngongenabo ubulungiswa futhi siholele endleleni elungile"
  38,23,"Ngempela lona ngumfowethu unezimvukazi ezingamashumi ayisishiyagalolunye nesishiyagalolunye mina nginemvukazi eyodwa, wayesethi, “nginike yona” futhi wangehlula ngempela"
  38,24,"Wathi (uDavide), “ngempela wenze okungenabo ubulungiswa kuwena ngokufuna imvukazi yakho ezimvukazini zakhe futhi ngempela baningi abahlanganyeli abacindezelana bodwa ngaphandle kwalabo abakholwayo futhi abenza okulungileyo futhi bambalwa labo” futhi uDavide wabona ukuthi simlingile, ngakho-ke wacela intethelelo eNkosini yakhe, wawa phansi wazithoba futhi waphendukela kuMvelinqangi ngokuzisola"
  38,25,Ngakho-ke samthethelela lokho futhi ngempela okwakhe ukusondela kuthina kanye nendawo yokuphindela enhle
  38,26,"Oh Davide! Ngempela thina sakwenza waba ngumholi emhlabeni ngakho-ke yehlulela phakathi kwabantu ngeqiniso futhi ungazilandeli izifiso zizokudukisa endleleni kaMvelinqangi, ngempela labo abadukayo endleleni kaMvelinqangi okwabo yisijeziso esinzima ngenxa yokuthi balikhohlwa usuku lokwahlulela"
  38,27,"Futhi asizange siwadale amazulu nomhlaba kanye nako konke okuphakathi kwawo ngaphandle kwenhloso, lokho wabona walabo abangakholwanga ngakho-ke usizi kulabo abangakholelwanga emlilweni"
  38,28,Noma nifisa ukuthi senze labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okuhle okulungileyo njengezoni emhlabeni noma senze abesaba (uMvelinqangi) njengabenzi bokubi na
  38,29,Yincwadi esayembula kuwena ibusisekile ukuze badlinze ngamavesi ayo futhi ukuze bakhumbule labo abaqondayo
  38,30,"Futhi sanikeza uDavide uSolomoni, inceku enhle kakhulu ngempelayenawayephendukela(kuMvelinqangingokuzisola)"
  38,31,Ngenkathi (amahhashi) ayeveziwe ngaphambili kwakhe kusihlwa aqeqeshwe kahle
  38,32,"Ngakho-ke wathi, “ngempela mina ngithande uthando lobuhle kunenkumbulo yeNkosi yami kwaze kwaba yilapho (ilanga) linyamalala esembozweni (sobumnyama)"
  38,33,"(Wathi), “wabuyiseleni kumina” wayeseqala ukuphulula imilenze kanye nezintamo (zamahhashi)"
  38,34,Futhi ngempela samlinga uSolomoni futhi sabeka phezulu kwesihlalo sakhe sobukhosi umzimba wayesephenduka ngokuzisola
  38,35,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami ngithethelele futhi ungiphe ubukhosi obungeke bufanele ngisho noma munye emva kwami, ngempela wena ungophayo”"
  38,36,Ngakho-ke sawenza umoya wamthobela waheleza ngempoqo yakhe noma ngabe yikuphi lapho ewuthumela khona
  38,37,Nabosathane bonke abakhi kanye nabatshuzi
  38,38,Kanye nabanye ababoshwe ngamaketango
  38,39,Lokhu yisipho sethu ngakho-ke yipha noma ugodle ngaphandle kokubala
  38,40,Futhi ngempela okwakhe ukusondela kuthina futhi indawo enhle yokuphindela
  38,41,"Futhi khumbula inceku yethu u-Ayub (uJobe) ngenkathi ememeza iNkosi yakhe (ethi), “ngempela usathane ungithinte ngenkathazo nangesijeziso"
  38,42,Gxoba ngonyawo lwakho lena yindawo yokugeza ebandayo kanye neyokuphuza
  38,43,Futhi samnikeza abantu bakhe (nabafana nabo kanye nabo) sabaphinda ngumusa ovela kuthina nesikhumbuzo salabo abaqondayo
  38,44,"Futhi thatha ngesandla sakho isixhawu sotshani bese ushaya ngaso umkakho futhi ungasephuli isethembiso sakho, ngempela samthola engobekezelayo, inceku enhle kakhulu ngempela yena wayengokuphendukayo ngokuzisola"
  38,45,Futhi khumbula izinceku zethu
  38,46,U-Abrahamu no-Isaka kanye noJakobe bangabantu bamandla kanye nombono
  38,47,Ngempela thina sabakhetha (ngokubanika) isikhumbuzo sendawo yokuhlala
  38,48,Futhi ngempela bona kuthina bangabanye babakhethiwe ukwedlula bonke
  38,49,"Futhi khumbula u-Ishmayeli no-Elisha no-Dhul-Kilf, Futhi bonke babengabanye babahle kakhulu"
  38,50,"Lesi\tyisikhumbuzo,\tfuthi\tngempela\tkwabakholwayo kunendawo enhle yokubuyela"
  38,51,Izivande zangunaphakade amasango azo ayobavulekela
  38,52,Bacambalale lapho phakathi bayomemeza lapho phakathi (becela) izithelo eziningi kanye nokuphuzwayo
  38,53,"Futhi eduzane kuyobe kunabesifazane abayobe bezithobile ekubhekeni, ontanga ngeminyaka"
  38,54,Lokhu yilokhu enethenjiswa kona kwelanga lokubala
  38,55,Ngempela lokhu yisabelo sethu esingeke siphele
  38,56,"Lokhu, futhi ngempela kwabenza okubi kunesiphetho esibi sokubuyela"
  38,57,"Isihogo bayongena kusona, yimbi leyondawo yokuphumula"
  38,58,Lokhu abakuzwe amanzi abilayo kanye nobovu
  38,59,Kanye nokunye kohlobo lwako
  38,60,"Leli yiqembu elingena kanye nani, angeke bemukelwe ngempela bona bayongena emlilweni"
  38,61,"Bayothi, “Chabo! Nina anemukelwe, nina nakuletha kuthina yimbi indawo yokuhlala”"
  38,62,"Futhi bayothi, “Nkosi yethu lowo owaletha lokhu kuthina ngakho-ke mnezelele ngesijeziso esiphindwe kabili emlilweni”"
  38,63,"Futhi bayothi, “kungani singawaboni amadoda (abantu) esasibabala phakathi kwabalungileyo"
  38,64,Ngakube sibathathe njengenhlekisa noma amehlo akakwazi ukubabona
  38,65,Ngempela lelo yiqiniso – ingxabano nokuphikisana kwabantu bomlilo
  38,66,"Ithi,“kuphelaminangingumxwayisifuthiakekhouNkulunkulu ekufanele akhonzwe ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi oyedwa umnqobi”"
  38,67,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nako konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili iphakeme ngamandla, iyathethelela"
  38,68,"Ithi, “loko kuyizindaba ezinkulu”"
  38,69,Nina enizifulathelayo
  38,70,Anginalo ulwazi ngabaholi (izinduna) eziphakeme ngenkathi ziphikisana
  38,71,Akwembulwanga lutho kumina ngaphandle kokuthi mina ngingumxwayisi ogqamile kuphela
  38,72,"Khumbula ngenkathi iNkosi yakho ithi ezingelosini, “ngempela mina ngingumdali womuntu ngobumba”"
  38,73,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sengimenzile ngamphefumulela ngomoya wami nabe seniwa phansi najabalala ngaphambili kwakhe
  38,74,Ngakho-ke izingelosi zaguqa ngokuzithoba zonke ndawonye
  38,75,Ngaphandle kuka-Iblis waqhosha futhi wabangomunye wabangakholwa
  38,76,"Wathi (uMvelinqangi), “Oh Iblis! Yini ekuvimbelayo ukuthi uthobele lowo engimdale ngezandla zami zombili na? Ngakube uziphakamisile noma ubengomunye walabo abaphakeme na"
  38,77,Wathi (u-Iblis) mina ngingcono kunaye ungidale ngomlilo wabe sewumdala ngobumba
  38,78,Wathi (uMvelinqangi) ngakho-ke phuma kulona (izulu) ngempela wena ungogxoshiweyo
  38,79,Futhi ngempela siphezu kwakho isiqalekiso sami kuze kube usuku lokwehlulela
  38,80,"Wathi (u-Iblis), “Nkosi yami nginike ithuba kuze kube usuku abayovuswa ngalo"
  38,81,(UMvelinqangi) wathi ngakho-ke ngempela wena ungomunye wabanikwe ithuba
  38,82,Kuze kube wusuku lwesikhathi esaziwayo
  38,83,"Wathi, “ngakho-ke ngokuhlonipheka kwakho ngempela ngizobadukisa bonke”"
  38,84,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zakho ezikhethiwe phakathi kwabo
  38,85,"Wathi, “yiqiniso futhi yiqiniso engilishoyo”"
  38,86,Ngempela ngizogcwalisa isihogo ngawe kanye nangabobonke abakulandelayo phakathi kwabo
  38,87,Ithi anginiceli umvuzo ngako futhi mina angiyena omunye wabakhohlisi
  38,88,Akuyilutho ngaphandle kwesikhumbuzo emihlabeni. 89. Futhi ngempela nizozazi izindaba zaso emva kwesikhashana
  39,1,Isambulo sencwadi sivela kuMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla onobuhlakani
  39,2,"Ngempela sayembula kuwena incwadi ngeqiniso, ngakho-ke khonza uMvelinqangi ube qotho kuyena enkolweni"
  39,3,"Ngokungangabazeki, ingekaMvelinqangi inkolo eqotho futhi labo abazithathele abavikeli esikhundleni sakhe (bathi) kuphela sibakhonzela ukuthi basisondeze eduzane noMvelinqangi ngempela uMvelinqangi akamholi lowo ongumqambi manga ongabongi"
  39,4,"Ukube uMvelinqangi wayethanda ukuthatha indondana wayezokhetha kulokho akudalayo akuthandayo, udumo malube kuye! Yena unguMvelinqangi oyedwa umnqobi"
  39,5,"Wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeqiniso, wenza ukuthi ubusuku bumboze imini futhi wenza ukuthi imini imboze ubusuku futhi wenza ilanga nenyanga kwathoba, konke kuhamba ngesikhathi esinqunyiwe ngokungangabazeki yena ungophakeme ngamandla ungothethelelayo"
  39,6,"Wanidala ngomphefumulo owodwa wabe esenza ngaye unkosikazi wakhe futhi wanehlisela phansi imfuyo engambili eyisishiyagalombili, unidala eziswini zabomama benu, indalo emva kwendalo ebumnyameni obuphindiwe kathathu lowo nguMvelinqangi iNkosi yenu bungobakhe ubukhosi akekho uNkulunkulu onokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe ngakho-ke niphendukiselwa kanjani emumva"
  39,7,"Uma ningakholwa ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi akanidingi futhi akakuthandi ukungakholwa ezincekwini zakhe futhi uma nibonga uyakuthokozela kunina, futhi akekho umthwali womthwalo oyothwala umthwalo womunye bese kuba seNkosini yenu ukubuyela kwenu bese iyanitshela ngaloko enanikwenza, ngempela yona iyisazi saloko okusezifubeni"
  39,8,"Futhi uma umuntu ethintwa ukhala kumvelinqangi ebheka kuye ecela intethelelo, kepha uma emupha emuseni wakhe, (umuntu) uyakhohlwa ukuthi ubekhala ngokuthintwa kwakhe, bese enza abahlanganyeli kanye no Mvelinqangi edukisa abantu kude nendlela ka-Allah. Ithi, “kujabulele nkungakholwa kwakho, nina yinina eningabangane besi hogo.”"
  39,9,"Kungabelowooqothophakathikobusukueguqilengokuzithoba futhi emile uqaphela impilo ezayo futhi uthembele emseni weNkosi yakhe ithi, “ngakube bayalingana yini labo abaziyo kanye nalabo abangazi na?” Kuphela yilabo abakhumbulayo abantu abaqondayo abathola ukukukweluleka"
  39,10,"Ithi, “Oh zinceku zami! lezo ezikholwayo yesabani iNkosi yenu” okwalabo abenza okuhle kakhulu kulomhlaba futhi umhlaba kaMvelinqangi ubanzi kuphela yilabo ababekezelayo abayokwemukela umvuzo wabo ngaphandle kwesibalo"
  39,11,"Ithi, “ngempela mina ngiphoqiwe ukuthi ngikhonze uMvelinqangi ngibeqotho enkolweni yakhe”"
  39,12,Futhi ngiphoqiwe ukuba ngibe ngowokuqala wabazinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi
  39,13,"Ithi, “ngempela mina ngiyesaba isijeziso sosuku olukhulu uma ngingayihloniphi iNkosi yami”"
  39,14,"Ithi, “uMvelinqangi engimkhonzayo ngiqotho enkolweni yakhe”"
  39,15,"Ngakho-ke khonzani loko enikuthandayo esikhundleni sakhe, ithi ngempela abalahlekelwe yilabo abalahlekelwe yimiphefumulo yabo kanye nabantu babo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo, ngempela loko ukulahlekelwa okucacile"
  39,16,"Okwabo kuyoba uphahla lomlilo ngaphezulu kwabo futhi nangaphansi kwabo izembozo (zomlilo) loko uMvelinqangi wesabisa ngako izinceku zakhe, Oh zinceku zami! ngakho-ke ngesabeni"
  39,17,Futhi labo abagwema izithixo hleze bazikhonze bese bephendukela kuMvelinqangi okwabo yizindaba ezinhle ngakho-ke memezela izindaba ezinhle ezincekwini zami
  39,18,Labo abalalela inkulumo bese belandela okuhle kwayo labo- ke bayilabo abaholwa nguMvelinqangi futhi labo bangabantu abaqondayo
  39,19,"Ngakube lowo eliqinisekile kuyena igama lesijeziso, ngakube wena ungamsindisa yini lowo osemlilweni"
  39,20,"Kepha labo abayesabayo iNkosi yabo okwabo ngamagumbi adephile elinye ngaphezulu kwelinye ngaphansi kwawo kugelezaimifula, yisethembisosikaMvelinqangi, uMvelinqangi akehluleki esethembisweni"
  39,21,"Awuboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni bese ewenza ukuthi angene ageleze njengeziphethu emhlabeni bese eveza ngawo izithelo ezinemibala eyehlukahlukene bese ziyabuna uzibone zibaphuzi bese ezenza ziba yizicucu, ngempela kuloko kunesikhumbuzo kubantu abaqondayo"
  39,22,"Ngakube lowo uMvelinqangi avule isifuba sakhe esivulela i-Islam (ukuzinikela ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi) usekukhanyeni okuvela eNkosini yakhe? ngakho-ke usizi kulabo izinhliziyo zabo ezilukhuni esikhumbuzweni, labo basekudukeni okucacile"
  39,23,"NguMvelinqangi owehlisela phansi inkulumo enhle kakhulu incwadi ziyefana ziphindaphindiwe, izikhumba zalabo abesaba iNkosi yabo ziyathuthumela bngayo bese izikhumba zabo kanye nezinhliziyo zabo ziyathamba enkumbulweni kaMvelinqangi, lokho ngukuhola kukaMvelinqangi, uhola ngako lowo amthandayo, futhi lowo uMvelinqangi amdukisayo ngakho-ke angeke abenaye umholi"
  39,24,Ngakube lowo oyobhekana ngobuso bakhe nesijeziso esibi ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo futhi kuyothiwa kwabayizoni yizwani loko nina enanikusebanzela
  39,25,Baphika labo ababengaphambilini kwabo ngakho-ke safika kubona isijeziso siqhamuka lapho bengaboni khona
  39,26,Ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi wabazwisa ihlazo empilweni yakulomhlaba futhi ngempela isijeziso sempilo ezayo sikhulu kakhulu ukube bebazi
  39,27,Futhi ngempela sabenzela abantu izibonelo kuleQur’an zazozonke izinhlobo ukuze bakhumbule
  39,28,IQur’an engesi-Arabhu engenabo ubuzombezombe ukuze bamesabe (uMvelinqangi)
  39,29,UMvelinqangi wenza isibonelo sendoda ephethwe ngabahlanganyeli abaphikisanayo kanye nendoda ephethwe ngokuphelele ngumphathi (oyedwa) ngakube bobabili bayefana? Udumiso malube kuMvelinqangi kepha iningi labo alazi
  39,30,Ngempela uzokufa futhi ngempela nabo bazokufa
  39,31,Bese ngempela nina ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo niyaphikisana ngaphambili kweNkosi yenu
  39,32,Ngakho-ke ngubani ongalungile kakhulu kunalowo oqambela uMvelinqangi amanga futhi aphike iqiniso kulapho selimfikele na? kanti akuson yini isihogo indawo yokuhlala abangakholwa na
  39,33,Futhi lowo olethe iqiniso futhi akholelwe kulona labo bangabamesabayo Umvelinqangi
  39,34,Okwabo kuyoba yinoma ngabe yintoni abayifisayo eNkosini yabo lowo ngumvuzo wabenzi bokuhle
  39,35,Ukuze uMvelinqangi asuse kubona okubi kakhulu kwaloko ababekwenza futhi abanike umvuzo wabo ngokuhle kakhulu kwaloko ababekwenza
  39,36,Ngakube uMvelinqangi akayanele yini inceku yakhe na? futhi bakwesabisa ngalabo (abakhonza abanye) esikhundleni sakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani uMvelinqangi amshiya ekudukeni ngakho-ke akanaye umholi
  39,37,"Futhi lowo oholwa nguMvelinqangi ngakho-ke akanaye umdukisi, akusiyena yini na uMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla ongumnini wokuphindisela"
  39,38,"Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba ngempelabazothi“ nguMvelinqangi” ithi“ ngakubenikubonile yini loko enikubizayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi uma uMvelinqangi efisa ukungihlupha ngakube loko kungakususa ukuhlupha kwakhe na? noma uma efisa ukungikhombisa umusa ngakube loko kungawugodla yini umusa wakhe na?” ithi “ uMvelinqangi unganele, bathembela kuyena abethembeli”"
  39,39,"Ithi “Oh Bantu bami! Sebenzani ngendlela yenu, ngempela nami ngiyisisebenzi ngakho-ke niyokwazi"
  39,40,Ukuthi ngubani esiza kuyena isijeziso esidumazayo futhi esivumeleke kuyena isijeziso esingapheliyo
  39,41,Ngempela sayembula kuwena incwadi siyembulela abantu ngeqiniso ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani oholekile kungokomphefumulo wakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani odukayo kuphela uzidukela yena futhi wena awusiyena umgadi wabo
  39,42,"UMvelinqangi uyayithatha imiphefumulo ngesikhathi sokufa kwayo kanye naleyo engafi ekulaleni kwayo bese eyayigodla leyo ayinqumele ukufa bese ethumela eminye esikhathini esinqunyiwe, ngempela kulokhu kunezimpawu kubantu abaziyo"
  39,43,Noma ngakube bazithathela abancengeli esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi? Ithi “ngisho noma ngabe bengenalutho futhi bengenawo umqondo
  39,44,"Ithi,“kungokukaMvelinqangikonkeukuncengela, ungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba bese nibuyiselwa kuyena”"
  39,45,Futhi uma uMvelinqangi ekhunjulwa yedwa ziyashwabana izinhliziyo zalabo abangakholelwa empilweni ezayo kepha uma kukhunjulwa labo abanye esikhundleni sakhe yilapho bona bejabula
  39,46,Ithi “Oh Mvelinqangi msunguli wamazulu nomhlaba isazi sokungabonwa nokubonwayo wena wehlulela phakathi kwezinceku zakho kuloko eziphikisana kukona”
  39,47,Futhi noma ngabe okwalabo abangalungile yikona konke okusemhlabeni kanye nokufana nako kanye nako banganikela ngako njengenhlengo ebubini besijeziso sosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo futhi kuyoba sobala kubona kuvela kuMvelinqangi loko abangakucabanganga
  39,48,Futhi kuyovela obala kubona ububi lobo ababusebenzela futhi kuyoqiniseka kubona loko ababenza ngako inhlekisa
  39,49,Kepha uma umuntu ethintwa ukulimala umemeza thina kuthi lapho uma simnika ububele obuvela kuthina athi kuphela nginikwe bona ngenxa yolwazi lwami qhabobo yisivivinyo kepha iningi labo alazi
  39,50,Ngempela bakusho loko labo ababengaphambilini kwabo ngakho-ke akuzange kubasize loko ababekusebenzela
  39,51,Ngakho-ke behlelwa okubi ababekusebenzela futhi labo abangalungile phakathi kwalabo bayokwehlelwa okubi abakusebenzela futhi bona angeke baphunyuke
  39,52,"Abazi yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi uyaselula isabelo kulowo amthandayo Futhiasinciphise, ngempelakulokokunezimpawu kubantu abakholwayo"
  39,53,"Ithi “Oh zinceku zami! Lezo ezazimosha imiphefumulo yazo, ningapheli ithemba emseni kaMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyazithethelela zonke izono, ngempela yena ungothethelelayo onesihawu”"
  39,54,Futhi phendukelani eNkosini yenu nizinikele kuyona ngaphambi kokuba isijeziso sifike kunina bese ningabi nakusizwa
  39,55,Futhi landelani okuhle kakhulu loko okwembulwa kunina okuvela eNkosini yenu ngaphambi kokuba sifike kunina isijeziso ngokuphazima kulapho nina ningaboni
  39,56,"Hleze umphefumulo uthi, “Oh ukuzisola kwami kuloko engangingakunakile mayelana noMvelinqangi futhi ngangingomunye walabo ababenza inhlekisa”"
  39,57,"Noma uthi, “ukube uMvelinqangi wayengiholile ngangizoba ngomunye wabalungileyo”"
  39,58,"Noma uthi ngenkathi ubona isijeziso, “ukube bengingaba nelinye ithuba bengingaba ngomunye wabenzi bokuhle”"
  39,59,Yebo! Ngempela amavesi ami afika kuwena kepha wawaphika futhi waqhosha wabe sewuba ngomunye wabangakholwa
  39,60,"Futhi ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo uyobona labo ababeqambela uMvelinqangi amanga ubuso babo buyobe benziwe mnyama, esihogweni ayikho yini indawo yokuhlala abaziphakamisayo"
  39,61,Futhi uMvelinqangi uyobasindisa labo abenza okulungileyo ngenxa yempumelelo yabo angeke bathintwe wokubi futhi bona angeke baphatheke kabi
  39,62,UMvelinqangi ngumdali wezinto zonke futhi yena ungumgadi ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke
  39,63,Ngezakhe izihluthulelo zamazulu nomhlaba futhi labo abangakholelwa emavesini kaMvelinqangi labo-ke bangabalahlekelwe
  39,64,"Ithi, “ngakube ningiphoqelela ekukhonzeni abanye onkulunkulu okungesiyena uMvelinqangi Oh nina eningazi”"
  39,65,"Futhi ngempela kwembulwa kuwena kanye nakulabo ababengaphambilini kwakho, uma wenzele uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni izenzo zakho zizobayize bese ubakulabo abalahlekelwe"
  39,66,Ngakho-ke khonza uMvelinqangi futhi ube ngomunye wababongayo
  39,67,"Futhi abasenzi isilinganiso (ngobunjalo) bukaMvelinqangi ngendlela ayiyona Futhi umhlaba wonke uyowubamba ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo futhi amazulu ayogoqwa esandleni sakhe sokudla, udumo malube kuye futhi uphakeme ngaphezulu kwaloko ababekwenza abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni"
  39,68,Futhikuyokhaliswaicilongobesebeyafabonkeabasemazulwini nabobonke abasemhlabeni ngaphandle kwalabo ngokuthanda kukaMvelinqangi bese liyakhaliswa ngesinye isikhathi bese kuba yilapho besukuma belinda
  39,69,"Futhi umhlaba uyocwebezela ngokukhanya kweNkosi futhi incwadi iyobekwa phansi futhi kuyolethwa abaphrofethi kanye nabofakazi, futhi kuyokwehlulelwa phakathi kwabo ngeqiniso futhi bona angeke benziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa"
  39,70,Futhi umphefumulo nomphefumulo uyokhokhelwa ngokuphelele loko owakwenza futhi yena (uMvelinqangi) wazi kangcono ngalokho ababekwenza
  39,71,Futhi labo abangakholwanga bayolethwa esihogweni beyizixuku kuze kube yilapho befika kusona futhi iyovulwa iminyango yaso futhi bayothi kubona abaqaphi baso “ngakube azifikanga yini kunina izithunywa eziphuma phakathi kwenu zinifundela amavesi eNkosi yenu futhi zinixwayisa ngokuhlangana kwalolusuku lwenu na?” bayothi “yebo” kepha liyogcwaliseka izwi lesijeziso kwabangakholwa
  39,72,"Kuyothiwa, “ngenani eminyangweni yesihogo nihlale lapho phakathi ingunaphakade, yimbi indawo yokuhlala abaqholoshayo”"
  39,73,Futhi labo abayesabayo iNkosi yabo bayolethwa esivandeni (ezulwini) beyizixuku kuze kube yilapho befika kulona futhi iyovulwa iminyango yalo futhi bayothi kubona abaqaphi balo “ukuthula makube kunina nenza kahle ngakho-ke ngenani kulona ingunaphakade”
  39,74,"Futhi bayothi “udumo malube kuMvelinqangi osifezile kuthina isethembiso sakhe futhi usenze saba yizindlalifa zezwe, sihlale ezulwini noma ngabe yikuphi lapho sithanda khona, muhle kakhulu umvuzo wabasebenzi"
  39,75,Futhiuyobonaizingelosizizungelezeisihlalo(sikaMvelinqangi) sobukhosi zigubha indumiso yeNkosi yazo futhi kuyokwehlulelwa phakathi kwazo ngeqiniso Futhi kuyothiwa “Udumo malube kuMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba”
  40,1,Ha Meem
  40,2,Isambulo sencwadi sivela kuMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla oyisazi
  40,3,"Umthetheleli wesono nomamukeli wokuzisola, onzima ekujeziseni, umnikazi womusa, ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe kukuyena ukubuyela"
  40,4,Abekho abaphikisanayo ngamavesi kaMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwalabo abangakholwanga ngakho-ke akungakukhohlisi ukuzulazula kwabo ezweni
  40,5,Abantu baNowa baphika ngaphambilini kwabo kanye namaqembu emva kwabo futhi zonke izizwe zahlosa ukuphambana nesithunywa sazo ukuze zisibambe Futhi ziphikise ngamanga ukuze zenze ngawo iqiniso libe yize ngakho-ke ngabathatha sasinjani isijeziso sami
  40,6,Futhi kanjalo laqiniseka izwi leNkosi yakho kulabo abangakholwanga ukuthi bona bangabangane bomlilo
  40,7,"Labo abathwele isihlalo sobukhosi kanye nalabo abasizungelezile, bagubha indumiso yeNkosi yakho futhi bakholelwa kuyona futhi bacelela labo abakholwayo intethelelo Nkosi yethu wengamele zonke izinto ngomusa nangolwazi ngakho-ke bathethelele labo abazisolayo futhi abalandela indlela yakho futhi baphephise esijezisweni sesihogo"
  40,8,"Nkosi yethu bangenise ezivandeni zaphakade lezo owabathembisa zona kanye noma ngabe ngubani olungile phakathi kobaba babo namakhosikazi abo kanye nenzalo yabo, ngempela wena ungophakeme ngamandla onobuhlakani"
  40,9,Futhi bavikele ebubini futhi noma ngabe ngubani omvikelayo ebubini ngalolusuku ngempela unomusa kuyena futhi lokho kuyimpumelelo enkulu
  40,10,Ngempela labo abangakholwanga bayobizwa “ngempela inzondo kaMvelinqangi yinkulu kakhulu kunenzondo yenu kunina uqobo ngenkathi nibizelwa enkolweni kepha nanenqaba
  40,11,"Bathi Nkosi yethu usenze ukuthi sife kabili futhi wasiphilisa kabili ngakho-ke siyazivuma izono zethu, ngakube ikhona yini indlela yokuphuma na"
  40,12,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi ngenkathi uMvelinqangi emenyezwa yedwa anizange nikholwe kepha kwathi uma behlanganiswa naye abahlanganyeli nabe seniyakholwa ngakho-ke ukwehlulela kungokukaMvelinqangi ophakeme omkhulu
  40,13,Nguyena onikhombisa izimpawu zakhe futhi onehlisela phansi isabelo esivela ezulwini futhi akekho okhumbulayo ngaphandle kwalowo ophendukayo
  40,14,Ngakho-ke bizani uMvelinqangi nibe qotho kuyena enkolweni yize noma ngabe bengakuthandi loko abangakholwa
  40,15,"Uphakeme ngamazinga, umnikazi wesihlalo sobukhosi, wenza ukuthi umoya wehlele kulowo amthandayo ezincekwini zakhe ngempoqo yakhe ukuze axwayise ngosuku lokuhlangana"
  40,16,"Ngosuku abayovela ngalo, akukho lutho olwabo oluyofihleka kuMvelinqangi, ungokabani umbuso ngalolusuku na? ungokaMvelinqangi oyedwa umnqobi"
  40,17,"Ngalolusuku yonke imiphefumulo izonikwa umvuzo ngalokho ekusebenzele angeke kwenziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa ngalolusuku, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyashesha ekubaleni"
  40,18,"Futhi baxwayise ngosuku olusondelayo lapho izinhliziyo ziyobe zisemiphinjeni, abangalungile angeke babe nomngane futhi angeke babenomncengeli oyohlonishwa"
  40,19,Uyakwazi okungumkhohlisi wamehlo kanye naloko okufihlwa yisifuba
  40,20,Futhi uMvelinqangi wehlulela ngeqiniso futhi labo abababizayo esikhundleni sakhe abehluleli lutho! Ngempela uMvelinqangi ungozwayo obonayo
  40,21,Abazange yini bahambe emhlabeni ukuze babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho salabo ababengaphambilini kwabo bona babenamandla amakhulu kunabo futhi beqatha uMvelinqangi ngezono zabo futhiabazange babenaye owayezobavikela kuMvelinqangi
  40,22,"Lokho kungenxa yokuthi zazifika kubona izithunywa zabo namavesi acacile kepha abakholwanga ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi wababamba ngempela yena unamandla, unzima ekujeziseni"
  40,23,Futhi ngempela samthumela uMose namavesi ethu kanye negunya elicacile
  40,24,Kufaro nakuHaman nakuKarun ngakho-ke bathi “umlumbi onamanga”
  40,25,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esebafikela neqiniso elivela kuthina bathi “bulalani amadodana alabo abakholwayo kanye naye, niyeke abesifazane babo” futhi icebo labangakholwa aliyilutho ngaphandle kokuduka"
  40,26,Futhi uFaro wathi “ngiyekeni ngimbulale uMose ukuze abize iNkosi yakhe ngempela mina ngiyesaba ukuthi uzoyiguqula inkolo yenu noma enze ukuganga emhlabeni”
  40,27,Futhi uMose wathi “ngempela mina ngifune isiphephelo eNkosini yami neNkosi yenu kubona bonke abaziqhenyayo akakholelwa osukwini lokubala (lokwahlulela)”
  40,28,"Futhi indoda ekholwayo emndenini kaFaro eyayifihle ukholo lwayo yathi ngakube nibulala indoda ngenxa yokuthi ithi “iNkosi yami nguMvelinqangi futhi ngempela inilethele izimpawu ezicacile ezivela eNkosini yenu, futhi uma iqamba amanga ngakho-ke aphezulu kwayo amanga ayo futhi uma ineqiniso nizokwehlelwa okunye kwaloko anethembisa kona ngempela uMvelinqangi akamholi lowo omoshayo ongumqambimanga"
  40,29,"Oh Bantu bami! Ungowenu umbuso namhlanje ningababusi emhlabeni ngakho-ke ngubani ozosivikela esijezisweni sikaMvelinqangi uma sifika kuthina? UFaro wathi, “anginikhombisi lutho ngaphandle kwengikubonayo futhi anginiholeli (kwenye indawo) ngaphandle kwasendleleni yokulunga”"
  40,30,Futhi lowo owayekholwa wathi “Oh bantu bami! ngempela mina ngiyanesabela okufana nosuku lwezixuku”
  40,31,Njengesiphetho sabantu baNowa naba A’d nabaThamud kanye nalabo ababengemumva kwabo futhi uMvelinqangi akakuthandi ukungabi nobulungiswa ezincekwini
  40,32,Futhi Oh Bantu bami! Ngempela mina ngiyanesabela usuku lokubizana
  40,33,"Ngosuku eniyofulathela ngalo nibaleka, aninaye umvikeli kuMvelinqangi futhi lowo odukiswa nguMvelinqangi ngakho- ke akanaye umholi"
  40,34,"Futhi ngempela uJosefa wafika kunina ngaphambilini nezimpawu ezicacile kepha naqhubeka nokuba sekungabazeni kuloko ayenifikele nako, kwaze kwaba uyafa nathi “uMvelinqangi akasoze asithumele isithunywa ngemva kwakhe” Kanjalo uMvelinqangi umshiya ekudukeni lowo omoshayo ongabazayo"
  40,35,"Labo abaphikisanayo ngamavesi kaMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwegunya elafika kubona, kuzonde kakhulu kuMvelinqangi kanye nakulabo abakholwayo kanjalo uMvelinqangi uyayisicilela inhliziyo yalowo nalowo oqhoshayo ocindezelayo"
  40,36,"Futhi uFaro wathi, “Oh Haman! Ngakhele isakhiwo esiphakeme ukuze ngithole izindlela”"
  40,37,Izindlela zezulu ukuze ngikhuphukele kuNkulunkulu kaMose futhi ngempela ngicabanga ukuthi ungumqambi manga futhi kanjalo kwenziwa kuFaro babukeka bubuhle ububi bomsebenzi wakhe wayesevinjelwa endleleni futhi icebo likaFaro lalingeyilutho ngaphandle kokubhubha
  40,38,"Futhi lowo owayekholwa wathi, “Oh Bantu bami! ngilandeleni ngizoniholela endleleni elungile”"
  40,39,Oh Bantu bami! Kuphela lempilo yalomhlaba yinjabulo futhi ngempela impilo ezayo yindawo yokuphumula
  40,40,Noma ngabe ngubani owenza okubi angeke anikwe umvuzo ngaphandle kokufana nako futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza okulungileyo engowesilisa noma engowesifazane futhi yena eyikholwa ngakho-ke labo bayongena esivandeni (ezulwini) bayokwabelwa khona ngaphandle kwesilinganiso
  40,41,Futhi Oh Bantu bami! Kungani ukuthi mina nginimemela ensindisweni kulapho nina ningimemela emlilweni
  40,42,Ningimemela ukuthi ngingakholwa kuMvelinqangi futhi ngimenzele abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni lokho engingenalo ulwazi lwako futhi mina nginimemela kophakeme ngamandla umthetheleli
  40,43,"Ngempela ningibizela kuloko ekungafanelwe kubizwe kulomhlaba ngisho nasempilweni ezayo\tfuthi ukuphindela kwethu kukuMvelinqangi futhi izoni zona zingabangane bomlilo"
  40,44,"Ngakho-ke niyokukhumbula loko engikushoyo kunina, futhi udaba lwami ngilubeka kuMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi ungumboni wezinceku"
  40,45,Ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi wamvikela ebubini balokho ababekuceba futhi saqiniseka kubantu baFaro isijeziso esibi
  40,46,Umlilo bayolethwa kuwona ekuseni nakusihlwa futhi ngosuku eliyofika ngalo ihora (kuyothiwa) “ngenisani abantu baFaro esijezisweni esinzima”
  40,47,Futhi khumbula ngenkathi beyophikisana emlilweni ngakho- ke bayothi ababuthakathaka kulabo ababezigabisa “ngempela thina sasingabalandeli benu ngakube nizoyiqhelelanisa nathi yini na ingxenye yomlilo?”
  40,48,"Bayothi labo ababezigabisa, “ngempela sonke siphakathi kuwona, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyehlulela phakathi kwezinceku”"
  40,49,"Futh labo abasemlilweni bayothi kubagadi besihogo, “bizani iNkosi yenu isenzele lula isijeziso sosuku olulodwa”"
  40,50,"Bayothi, “azizange yini na zifike kunina izithunywa zenu namavesi acacile?” bayothi,“yebo” bayothi “ngakho-ke memezani futhi akuyilutho ukumemeza kwabangakholwa ngaphandle kokuduka nje"
  40,51,Ngempela thina siyazelekelela izithunywa zethu kanye nalabo abakholwayo empilweni yakulomhlaba nangosuku abayosukuma ngalo ofakazi
  40,52,Ngosuku lapho lingeke libasize abangalungile izaba labo futhi okwabo yisiqalekiso futhi okwabo yindawo embi yokuhlala
  40,53,Futhi ngempela samnikeza uMose ukuholwa futhi sabenza abantwana bakwa-Israyeli ukuthi babeyizindlalifa zencwadi
  40,54,Ukuhola kanye nesikhumbuzo kubantu abaqondayo
  40,55,"Ngakho-ke bekezela, ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso futhi cela intethelelo esonweni sakho futhi ugubhe indumiso yeNkosi yakho kusihlwa nasekuseni"
  40,56,"Ngempela labo abaphikisanayo ngamavesi kaMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwegunya elafika kubona, akukho lutho ezifubeni zabo ngaphandle kokuqhenya abangeke babenako ngakho-ke funa isiphephelo kuMvelinqangi ngempela yena ungozwayo obonayo"
  40,57,Ngempela ukudalwa kwamazulu nomhlaba kukhulu kakhulu kunokudalwa kwabantu kepha iningi labantu alazi
  40,58,"Futhi ayifani impumputhe nobonayo kanye nalabo abakholwayo futhi abenza okulungile nabenza okubi, kuncane loko enikukhumbulayo"
  40,59,Ngempela ihora liyeza akukho ukungabaza kulona kepha iningi labantu alikholwa
  40,60,"Futhi iNkosi yenu yathi, “ ngimemezeni ngizoniphendula, ngempela labo abadelela ukukhonzwa kwami bayongena esihogweni bejabhisiwe”"
  40,61,"UMvelinqangi nguyena owanenzela ubusuku ukuthi niphumule kubona nemini ukuze nibone, ngempela uMvelinqangi ugcwele umusa kubantu kepha iningi labantu alibongi"
  40,62,"Lowo nguMvelinqangi iNkosi yenu umdali wezinto zonke, ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe niphendukelani emumva na"
  40,63,Kanjalo baphendukela emumva labo ababephika amavesi kaMvelinqangi
  40,64,"NguMvelinqangi owanibekela umhlaba njengendawo yokuphumulakanyenamazuluabayisakhiwowayeseyanibumba nabayisimo senu esihle futhi wanabela ezintweni ezinhle, lowo nguMvelinqangi iNkosi yenu ngakho-ke ubusisekile uMvelinqangi, iNkosi yemihlaba"
  40,65,"Ungophilayo, ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe ngakho-ke bizani yena nibe qotho kuyena enkolweni, udumo malube kuMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba"
  40,66,"Ithi, “ngempela ngenqatshelwe ukuthi ngikhonze labo enibakhonzayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi ngenkathi kufika kunina amavesi acacile avela eNkosini yami futhi ngiphoqiwe ukuthi ngizinikele eNkosini yemihlaba"
  40,67,"Yena uyilowo owanidala ngothuli kwasekuba yingesidoda kwasekubaingehlulebeseenikhiphaniyizinganebeseniyakhula nifinyelele ekubeni semandleni enu bese niba badala, futhi phakathi kwenu kunabafayo ngaphambi (kwalokhu) futhi nifinyelele esikhathini esinqunyiwe futhi ukuze niqonde"
  40,68,Nguyena ophilisayo futhi obulalayo ngakho-ke uma enquma udaba kuphela uthi kulona “ yenzeka” bese kuyenzeka
  40,69,Awuboni yini labo abaphikisanayo ngamavesi kaMvelinqangi ukuthi baphendukiselwa kanjani emumva
  40,70,Labo abaqamba amanga ngencwadi nangalokho esakuthumela nesithunywa bayokwazi
  40,71,Ngenkathi iziphika zensimbi zisezintanyeni zabo kanye namaketango abayodonswa ngawo
  40,72,Emanzini abilayo bese beshiswa emlilweni
  40,73,"Bese kuthiwa kubona, “ kuphi lokho enanenzela ngako uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni"
  40,74,"Esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bayothi, “banyamalele kuthina kepha sasingamemezi lutho ngaphambilini, kanjalo uMvelinqangi uyabadukisa abangakholwa"
  40,75,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi naniziphakamisa emhlabeni ngaphandle kweqiniso nangenxa yokuthi nanijabula
  40,76,"Ngenani emasangweni esihogo nihlale phakathi ingunaphakade, yimbi indawo yoku abaqholoshayo"
  40,77,"Ngakho-ke bekezela, ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso noma sikubonisa ingxenye yaloko esibathembisa kona noma siyakubulala ngakho-ke kukuthina ukubuyiselwa kwabo"
  40,78,"Futhi ngempela sazithumela izithunywa ngaphambilini kwakho phakathi kwazo kunalezo esikutshelile ngomlando wazo futhi phakathi kwazo kunalezo esingazange sikutshele umlando wazo futhi kwakungesikona okwesithunywa ukuthi size nophawu (noma ivesi) ngaphandle kwemvume kaMvelinqangi, ngakho-ke uma kufika impoqo kaMvelinqangi kwehlulelwa ngeqiniso futhi bazolahlekelwa abalandeli bamanga"
  40,79,NguMvelinqangi owanenzela imfuyo ukuze nigibele kuzona nenze nezinye izidingo futhi nidle kuzona
  40,80,Futhi kuzona ninenzuzo ukuze nifinyelele ngazo ezidingweni ezisezifubeni zenu futhi phezulu kwazo naphezulu kwemikhumbi niyathwalwa
  40,81,Futhi uyanikhombisa izimpawu zakhe ngakho-ke yiziphi izimpawu zikaMvelinqangi eniziphikayo
  40,82,"Ngakube abahambi yini emhlabeni ukuze babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho salabo ababengaphambilini kwabo, babebaningi kunabo futhi benamadla amakhulu nangezindlela ezweni, ngakho-ke akubasizanga lokho ababekusebenzela"
  40,83,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sezifika kubona izithunywa zabo namavesi acacile bathokoza ngalokho okwakukanye nabo okolwazi kwase kuyaqiniseka kubona lokho ababenza ngako inhlekisa
  40,84,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebesibona isijeziso sethu bathi sikholiwe kuMvelinqangi yedwa futhi siyakuphika lokho esasenzelangakouMvelinqangiabahlanganyeliekumkhonzeni
  40,85,"Kepha akuzange kubasize ukukholwa kwabo kwathi lapho sebesibona isijeziso sethu, yindlela kaMvelinqangi eseyadlula ezincekwini zakhe futhi lapho balahlekelwe abangakholwa"
  41,1,Ha meem
  41,2,Isambulo esivela konomusa onesihawu
  41,3,"Incwadi, enziwe acaca amavesi ayo iQur’an engesi-arabhu yabantu abaziyo"
  41,4,Iletha izindaba ezimnandi futhi ingumxwayisi kepha liyafulathela iningi labo ngakho-ke bona abezwa
  41,5,"Futhi bathi “izinhliziyo zethu zingaphansi kwezembozo kulokho osimemela kukona futhi ezindlebeni zethu kunobuthulu futhi phakathi kwethu nawe kunesisitho, ngakho-ke sebenza (ngendlela yakho) ngempela nathi siyasebenza”"
  41,6,"Ithi, kuphela mina ngingumuntu njengani kwembuliwe kumina ukuthi uNkulunkulu wenu nguNkulunkulu oyedwa ngakho-ke yibani ngabaqondile kuyena futhi nicele intethelelo yakhe futhi usizi kwabenzela uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni"
  41,7,Labo abangayikhokhi izakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhelwa abampofu) futhi bona bengakholwelwa empilweni ezayo
  41,8,Ngempela labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okulungileyo okwabo ngumvuzo ongapheliyo
  41,9,"Ithi “ngukube ngempela nina anikholwa kulowo owadala umhlaba ezinsukwini ezimbili na? Futhi nimbekela izimbangi, lowo yiNkosi yemihlaba”"
  41,10,Futhi yabeka kuwona izintaba ngaphezulu kwawo futhi yawubusisa futhi kuwona yenza ukudla (kwezihlali) zawo ezinsukwini ezine (ukuze bazi) labo ababuzayo
  41,11,"Yabe seyiphendukela ezulwini lona laliyintuthu yabeseyithi kulona nasemhlabeni “wozani nobabili nithanda noma ningathandi” kokubili kwathi, “siyeza sithanda”"
  41,12,"(INkosi yemihlaba) yabe seyikuqeda ukukwakha kwaba ngamazulu ayisikhombisa ezinsukwini ezimbili futhi yembula kulelo nalelozulu udaba lwalo futhi sahlobisa izulu elingezansi ngezibani kanye nokulondolozeka, leso yisimiso sophakeme ngamandla, isazi"
  41,13,Ngakho-ke uma befulathela ithi “nginexwayisile ngesehlakalo esifana nesehlakalo sika-A’D noThamud
  41,14,"Ngenkathi zifika kubona izithunywa ziqhamuka ngaphambili kwabo nangemumva kwabo zathi “ningakhonzi lutho ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi” bathi, “ukube iNkosi yethu yayithanda yayizokwehlisela phansi izingelosi, ngakho-ke thina singabangakholelwa kulokho enithunywe kona”"
  41,15,"Mayelana noA’D, babezikhukhumeza emhlabeni ngokungesilona iqiniso futhi bathi,“ngubani onamandla amakhulu ukwedlula thina?, Ababoni yini ukuthi nguMvelinqangi owabadala, yena unamandla amakhulu ngaphezulu kwabo futhi babewaphika amavesi ethu"
  41,16,Ngakho-ke sathumela kubona umoya onamandla ezinsukwini zeshwa ukuze sibazwise isijeziso esiyihlazo empilweni yakulomhlaba futhi isijeziso sempilo ezayo siyihlazo kakhulu futhi bona angeke balekelelwe
  41,17,"Futhi mayelana (nabantu) ba-Thamud sabahola, kepha bathanda ubumpumputhe kunokuholwa, ngakho-ke sabathatha isehlakalo sesijeziso esiyihlazo ngenxa yaloko ababekwenza"
  41,18,Futhi sabasindisa labo ababekholwa futhi abagwema ububi
  41,19,Futhi khumbula ngosuku lapho ziyobe ziqoqelwa emlilweni izitha zikaMvelinqangi ziyoqhutshelwa phambili
  41,20,Kuze kube yilapho uma zifika kusona ukuzwa kwazo (amadlebe azo) namehlo azo kanye nezikhumba zazo ziyofakaza maqondana nazo mayelana naloko ababekwenza
  41,21,"Futhi (izitha zikaMvelinqangi) ziyothi ezikhumbeni zazo, “kungani nifakaza ngathi na? izindlebe zazo namehlo azo kanye nezikhumba zazo ziyothi, “nguMvelinqangi osenze ukuthi sikhulume lowo okunguyena owenza zonke izinto ukuthi zikhulume futhi yena wanidala ekuqaleni futhi niyobuyiselwa kuyena"
  41,22,"Futhi naningawambozi hleze amadlebe enu namehlo enu kanye nezikhumba zenu kufakaze maqondana nani, kepha nanicabanga ukuthi uMvelinqangi wayengazi kakhulu ngaloko enanikwenza"
  41,23,Futhi lokho ngumcabango wenu lowo enaniwucabanga ngeNkosi yenu yanibhubhisa ngakho-ke nabangabanye babalahlekelwe
  41,24,Ngakho-ke uma bebekezela umlilo yindawo yabo yokuhlala futhi uma befuna ukuthokozisa (uMvelinqangi) ngakho-ke bona abayibona balabo abavunyelwe ukuthokozisa
  41,25,"Futhi sababela abangane abakhulu, abenza kwabukeka kukuhle kubona lokho okwakungaphambili kwabo kanye nalokho okwakungemumva kwabo futhi yaqiniseka kubona inkulumo njengoba yaqiniseka ezizweni esezadlula ngaphambilini kwabo (izizwe) zamajinn kanye nabantu, ngempela bona babelahlekelwe"
  41,26,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi, “ningayilaleli leQur’an futhi nenze umsindo uma ifundwa ukuze ninqobe”"
  41,27,Ngakho-ke ngempela siyobazwisa labo abangakholwanga isijeziso esinzima futhi ngempela siyobanika umvuzo wokubi kakhulu lokho ababekwenza
  41,28,"Lowo ngumvuzo wezitha zikaMvelinqangi – umlilo, okwabo lapho phakathi kuyoba yikhaya langunaphakade (lokhu) yinkokhelo ngenxa yokuthi babephika amavesi ethu"
  41,29,"Futhi\tlabo\tababengakholwa\tbayothi,\t“Nkosi\tyethu sikhombise labo abasidukisa abangama-jinn nabantu ukuze bobabili sibabeke ngaphansi kwezinyawo zethu ukuze babengaphansi kunabobonke”"
  41,30,"Ngempela labo abathi, “iNkosi yethu nguMvelinqangi” bese beyaqonda zehlele kubona Izingelosi, ningesabi futhi ningaphatheki kabi kepha yemukelani izindaba ezimnandi zesivande enanethenjiswe sona"
  41,31,Thina singabangane benu empilweni yalomhlaba kanye nakwezayo futhi okwenu lapho phakathi (esivandeni) yinoma ngabe yini imiphefumulo yenu ekufisayo futhi okwenu phakathi kusona yinoma ngabe yintoni eniyifunayo
  41,32,Injabulo evela kothethelelayo onesihawu
  41,33,"Futhi ngubani ongcono kakhulu enkulumweni kunalowo omemela kuMvelinqangi futhi enze okulungileyo futhi athi, ngempela mina ngingomunye wabazithobile ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi"
  41,34,"Futhi akufani okuhle nokubi, vimba ngaloko okuhle kakhulu kulapho lowo ophakathi kwakho naye kunobutha kube sengathi yena ungumngane osondele"
  41,35,Futhi akekho oyonikwa kona (okuhle) ngaphandle kwalabo ababekezelayo futhi akekho oyonikwa kona ngaphandle komnikazi wenhlanhla enkulu
  41,36,Futhi uma usathane ekuchezukisa ngakho-ke funa isiphephelo kuMvelinqangi ngempela yena ungozwayo owaziyo
  41,37,Futhi ezinye zezimpawu zakhe ubusuku nemini nelanga nenyanga ningaliguqeli ilanga nenyanga kepha guqelani uMvelinqangi okunguyena owadala kona uma kungukuthi nguyena enimkhonzayo
  41,38,Kepha uma bezikhukhumeza ngakho-ke labo abaseNkosini yabo bayayidumisa ubusuku nemini futhi bona abakhathali
  41,39,"Futhi ezinye zezimpawu zakhe ukuthi ubona umhlaba awutheli lutho kwaba yilapho sehlisela phezulu kwawo amanzi uyanyakaza futhi ukhukhumale, ngempela lowo owuphilisayo ungumphilisi wokufile ngempela yena wenza zonke izinto"
  41,40,"Ngempela labo abaphendukezela amavesi ethu abafihlekile kuthina, ngakube lowo ophonswa emlilweni ungcono noma uza ephephilengosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo yenzani lokho enikufisayo ngempela yena (uMvelinqangi) ubona konke enikwenzayo"
  41,41,Ngempela labo abangakholelwanga esikhumbuzweni kulapho sesifikile kubona futhi ngempela sona siyincwadi ephakeme ngezinga
  41,42,Amanga akezi kuyona ngaphambili kwayo nangemumva kwayo isambulo esivela konobuhlakani odunyiswayo
  41,43,"Akukho lutho olushiwoyo kuwena ngaphandle kwaloko okwashiwo esithunyweni ngaphambilini kwakho, ngempela iNkosi yakho ngumnikazi wentethelelo futhi ngumnikazi wesijeziso esibuhlungu"
  41,44,"Futhi ukube besiyenzile iQur’an ngolimi lakwelinye izwe ngempela babezokuthi, “ kungani ingachazwanga imininingwane yamavesi ayo? Kungani hhayi ngesi-Arabhu kanye nom’Arabhu?” ithi yona eyalabo abakholwayo, umholi kanye nomelaphi futhi labo abangakholwa ezindlebeni zabo kunobuthuli futhi bona (ubuthuli) kuwubumpumputhe kubona, labo-ke babizwa endaweni ekude"
  41,45,"Futhi ngempela samnikeza uMose incwadi kwase kuvela impikiswano kuyo futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yegama elaselidlulile elivela eNkosini yakho, ngempela kwakuzokwehlulelwa phakathi kwabo futhi ngempela bona basekungabazeni okukhulu ngayo"
  41,46,Noma ngabe ngubani owenza okulungileyo ngakho-ke kungokomphefumulo wakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza okubi ngakho-ke kuphambene naye futhi iNkosi yakho ayinako ukungabi nobulungiswa ezincekwini
  41,47,"Luqondene naye ulwazi lwehora futhi asikho isithelo esiphumayo ekhasini laso futhi akekho owesifazane okhulelwayo noma azale ngaphandle kolwazi lwakhe futhi ngosuku lapho ebabiza (ethi) “baphi abahlanganyeli bami bayothi, “ siyamemezela kuwena ukuthi akekho phakathi kwethu ufakazi”"
  41,48,Futhi kuyonyamalala kubona lokho ababekubiza ngaphambilini futhi bayocabanga ukuthi abanayo indawo yokukhosela
  41,49,Umuntu akakhathali ukucela okuhle kepha uma ethintwa okubi uphatheka kabi aphelelwe yithemba
  41,50,"Futhi uma simzwisa umusa ovela kuthina emva kokuba ukuhlupheka sekumthintile ngempela uthi, “lokhu kungokwami futhi angicabangi ukuthi ihora liyofika futhi uma ngiphindiselwe"
  41,51,"eNkosini yami ngempela okwami okuhle kakhulu kuyona, ngakho-ke ngempela siyobatshela labo abangakholwanga ngalokho ababekwenza futhi ngempela siyobazwisa isijeziso esinzima"
  41,52,Futhi uma sikhombisa umusa kumuntu uyahoxa futhi afulathele kepha uma ethintwa okubi wenza umthandazo omude
  41,53,"Ithi, “ngakube nibonile yini uma ivela kuMvelinqangi (iQur’an) nabeseniyayiphika, ngakube ngubani oduke kakhulu kunalowo osekuhlubukeni okukude le!”"
  41,54,"Siyobakhombisa izimpawu zethu emhlabeni kanye nasemiphefumulweni yabo kuze kube sobala kubona ukuthi yona iyiqiniso, ngakube akwanele yini ukuthi iNkosi yakho yona ingufakazi phezulu kwezinto zonke? 55. Bheka! Ngempela bona basekungabazeni mayelana nokuhlangana ne Nkosi yabo, Bheka! Ngempela yona ingamele zonke izinto"
  42,1,Ha Meem
  42,2,Ain Sin Qaf
  42,3,"Kanjalo uyakwembula kuwena kanye nakulaba ababengaphambilini kwakho, nguMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla onobuhlakani"
  42,4,"Kungokwakhe noma ngabe yini esemazulwini kanye noma ngabe yini esemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme kakhulu, mkhulu"
  42,5,Amazulu angase adabuke phakathi ngaphezulu kwawo futhi izingelosi zigubha indumiso yeNkosi yazo futhi zicelela labo abasemhlabeni intethelelo bheka! Ngempela uMvelinqangi yena ungothethelelayo onesihawu
  42,6,"Futhi labo abathatha (abanye) abavikeli esikhundleni sakhe, uMvelinqangi ungumlondolozi phezulu kwabo futhi wena awusiyena umphathi phezulu kwabo"
  42,7,"Futhi kanjalo siyembulile kuwena iQur’an ngesi-Arabhu ukuze uxwayise unina wamadolobha kanye noma ngabe ngobani abawazungelezile futhi uxwayise ngosuku lokuhlangana, akukho ukungabaza ngalo, ingxenye iyokuba sesivandeni futhi (enye) ingxenye ibe semlilweni ovuthayo"
  42,8,Futhi ukube uMvelinqangi wayethanda wayezobenza isizwe esisodwa kepha ufaka lowo amthandayo emseni wakhe futhi izoni azinaye umvikeli noma umsizi
  42,9,"Noma ngakube bazithathela abavikeli esikhundleni sakhe, kepha nguMvelinqangi ongumvikeli futhi yena uphilisa abafile futhi yena wenza zonke izinto"
  42,10,"Futhi noma ngabe yini eniphikisana kuyona, ngakho-ke isehlulelo sayo sikuMvelinqangi, lowo nguMvelinqangi iNkosi yami ngethembele kuyena futhi ngiphendukela kuyona ngokuzisola"
  42,11,"Umdali wamazulu nomhlaba wanenzela phakathi kwenu ngakubili futhi nasezinkomeni ngakubili, uyaniphindaphinda akukho lutho olufana naye futhi yena ungozwayo obonayo"
  42,12,"Ngezakhe izihluthulelo zamazulu nomhlaba. Uyaselula isabelo kunoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo futhi anciphise, ngempela yena uyisazi sazo zonke izinto"
  42,13,"UMvelinqangi wanibekela inkolo leyo ayibekela uNowa kanye naleyo esiyembulile kuwena kanye nesayembula ku- Abrahamu nakuMose kanye nakuJesu ukuthi baqinise inkolo, futhi ningaqembukelani kuyona, kunzima kulabo abakhonza izithombe lokho enibamemela kukona, uMvelinqangi uziqokela lowo amthandayo futhi uholela kuyena lowo ophendukela kuyena ngokuzisola"
  42,14,"Futhi babengaqembukelene kwaze kwaba yingaphambili kokuba sebefikelwe ulwazi ngenxa yomona nenzondo phakathi kwabo futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yegama eselidlulile elivela eNkosini yakho esikhathini esimisiwe kwakuzokwehlulelwa phakathi kwabo, futhi ngempela labo ababenziwe ukuthi badle ifa lencwadi emva kwabo ngempela basekungabazeni okunzima ngayo"
  42,15,"Ngakho-ke kulokho mema futhi ume uqine njengokuba uphoqiwe futhi ungalandeli izifiso zabo futhi ithi, “ngikholiwe kulokho okwembulwa nguMvelinqangi okuyincwadi futhi ngiphoqiwe ukuthi ngenze ubulungiswa phakathi kwenu, uMvelinqangi yiNkosi yethu neNkosi yenu, okwethu yimisebenzi yethu nokwenu yimisebenzi yenu, ayikho impikiswanophakathikwethunani, uMvelinqangiuyosiqoqela ndawonye futhi kukuyena ukuphindela kokugcina"
  42,16,Futhi labo abaphikisanayo ngoMvelinqangi emva kokuba sekwamukeliwe impikiswano yabo iyize leze eNkosini yabo futhi phezulu kwabo kunentukuthelo (kaMvelinqangi) futhi okwabo yisijeziso esinzima
  42,17,"NguMvelinqangi owembula incwadi ngeqiniso nangesikalo, futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi mhlawumbe ihora selisondele"
  42,18,Ukulisheshisa (ihora bayakufisa) labo abangakholelwa kulona kulapho labo abakholwayo belesaba futhi bayazi ukuthi lona liyiqiniso bheka! Ngempela labo abaphikisanayo mayelana nehora ngempela basekudukeni okukude le
  42,19,"UMvelinqangi unomusa ezincekwini zakhe wabela noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo futhi yena uqatha, ungophakeme ngamandla"
  42,20,Noma ngabe ngubani ofisa isivuno sempilo ezayo siyamunezelela esivunweni sakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani ofisa isivuno salomhlaba simunika sona futhi empilweni ezayo angeke abenayo ingxenye
  42,21,"Noma ngakube banabahlanganyeli ababamisele inkolo, lokho angakuvumelanga uMvelinqangi futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yegama lamanqamu ngempela kwakuzokwehlulelwa phakathi kwabo futhi ngempela izoni okwazo yisijeziso esibuhlungu"
  42,22,"Uyozibona izoni zesaba ngenxa yezakusebenzela futhi kona kwehlela kubona futhi labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okulungileyo bayokuba sezimfundeni zezivande, okwabo kuyoba yinoma ngabe yini abayifunayo ngaphambili kweNkosi yabo, lowo ngumusa omkhulu"
  42,23,"Lokho, yilokho uMvelinqangi akutshela izinceku zakhe njengezindaba ezinhle lezo ezakholwa futhi ezenza okulungileyo, ithi, “angiwuceli umvuzo kunina ngakho ngaphandle kothando ezihlotsheni zami nakunoma ngabe ngubani osebenzela okuhle siyomunezelela kukona okuhle, ngempela uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo obongayo"
  42,24,"Noma bathi, “uqambela uMvelinqangi amanga ngakho-ke uma uMvelinqangi ethanda uyayisicilela inhliziyo yakho, futhi uMvelinqangi uyawasusa amanga aqinisekise iqiniso ngamazwi akhe, ngempela yena uyisazi salokho okusezifubeni"
  42,25,Futhi nguyena owamukela ukuphenduka ezincekwini zakhe futhi othethelela izenzo ezimbi futhi (uMvelinqangi) uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo
  42,26,"Futhi uyabaphendula labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo futhi abanezelele emseni wakhe, futhi abangakholwa okwabo yisijeziso esinzima"
  42,27,"Futhi ukube uMvelinqangi wayeselulile isabelo sezinceku zakhe ngempela zazizohlubuka emhlabeni, kepha usehlisa ngendlela athanda ngayo ngempela yena ngezinceku zakhe uyazi uyabona"
  42,28,Futhi nguyena owehlisela phansi imvula emuva kokuba bephelelwe yithemba futhi awusabalalise umusa wakhe futhi yena ungumvikeli ofanele ukudunyiswa
  42,29,Futhi ezinye zezimpawu zakhe yindalo yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke akusakaza kukona kokubili (amazulu nomhlaba) okuyizidalwa ezinyakazayo futhi yena unawo amandla okubaqoqela ndawonye uma ethanda
  42,30,Futhi noma ngabe yiliphi ishwa elinivelelayo kungenxa yalokho izandla zenu ezikusebenzele futhi (uMvelinqangi) uyathethelela kakhulu
  42,31,Futhi nina aniyibona abaphunyukayo emhlabeni futhi aninaye umvikeli nomelekeleli ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi
  42,32,"Futhi ezimpawini zakhe imikhumbi olwandle, okusengathi yizintaba"
  42,33,"Uma ethanda uyawuthulisa umoya, bese (ulwandle) lunganyakazi endaweni yalo yangaphezulu, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kulowo nalowo obekezelayo, obongayo"
  42,34,"Noma ababhubhise ngenxa yalokho abakusebenzela, futhi uyathethelela kakhulu"
  42,35,Futhi bayazi labo abaphikisanayo ngamavesi ethu (ukuthi) abanayo indawo yokuphephela
  42,36,Ngakho-ke noma ngabe yini eninikwe yona yinjabulo yempilo yalomhlaba futhi lokho okukuMvelinqangi kungcono futhi kuyahlala kulabo abakholwayo futhi abathembela eNkosini yabo
  42,37,Kanye nalabo abagwema izono ezinkulu nokukhohlakala futhi okuthi uma bethukuthele bathethelele
  42,38,Nalabo abaphendulayo eNkosini yabo futhi abenza umthandazo futhi abenza udaba lwabo (lunqunywe) yisigungu phakathi kwabo futhi abasebenzisa kulokho esababela kona
  42,39,Nalabo okuthi uma behlelwa yingcindezelo baziphindiselele
  42,40,"Futhi umvuzo wokubi okubi okufana nako, ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani othethelelayo futhi alungise umvuzo wakhe ukuMvelinqangi, ngempela yena akazithandi izoni"
  42,41,Futhi ngempela noma ngabe ngubani oziphindiselayo emva kokuba ecindezelwe ngakho-ke labo abanayo indlela (yokusolwa)
  42,42,"Kuphela indlela (yokusolwa) ikulabo abenza okungenabo ubulungiswa kubantu, futhi abacindezelayo emhlabeni ngokungesilona iqiniso, labo-ke okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu"
  42,43,Futhi ngempela noma ngabe ngubani obekezelayo futhi athethelele ngempela lokho kuwukulungisa izindaba
  42,44,"Futhi lowo oshiywa nguMvelinqangi ekudukeni, ngakho-ke akanaye umvikeli emva kwakhe futhi uyobona izoni okuyothi uma sezibona isijeziso zithi, “ngakube ikhona yini indlela yokuphindela?”"
  42,45,"Futhi uyobona belethwa ngaphambili kwaso bethotshiswe yinjabhiso bebheka ngokujeqeza okufifiyelayo, futhi labo abakholwayo bayothi, “ngempela abalahlekelwe yilabo abalahlekelwa yimiphefumulo yabo kanye nemindeni yabo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo, bheka ngempela izoni zisesijezisweni esingapheliyo.”"
  42,46,Futhi angeke babenabo abavikeli abayobalekelela ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe ngubani uMvelinqangi amshiya ekudukeni akanayo indlela
  42,47,"Phendulani iNkosi yenu ngaphambi kokuba kufike usuku olungeke lugwenywe oluvela kuMvelinqangi, angeke nibe nesiphephelo ngalolosuku futhi angeke niphike"
  42,48,"Kepha uma befulathela, ngakho-ke asikuthumelanga kubona njengomlondolozi, awukho (umthwalo) ophezulu kwakho ngaphandle kokudlulisela (umyalezo) futhi ngempela uma sizwisa umuntu umusa ovela kuthina uyawuthokozela futhi uma behlelwa okubi ngenxa yalokho izandla zabo ezikulethe ngaphambili, ngakho-ke umuntu akabongi"
  42,49,"UngokaMvelinqangi umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba, udala noma ngabe yini ayithandayo, unikeza lowo amthandayo (ingane) yesifazane futhi unikeza lowo amthandayo (ingane) yesilisa"
  42,50,Noma abanike kokubili isilisa nesifazane futhi wenza inyumba noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo ngempela yena ungowaziyo owenza (izinto zonke)
  42,51,"Futhi akusikona okomuntu ukuthi uMvelinqangi akhulume naye ngaphandle kwesambulo noma ngemumva kwesembozo noma athumele isithunywa ukuze sembule ngentando yakhe noma ngabe yini ayithandayo, ngempela yena uphakeme unobuhlakani"
  42,52,"Futhi kanjalo sasembula kuwena isambulo ngempoqo yethu, wawungazi ukuthi yini incwadi noma inkolo, kepha sayenza yaba ukukhanya esihola ngako noma ngabe ngubani esimthandayo ezincekwini zethu futhi ngempela wena uholela endleleni eqondile"
  42,53,"Indlela kaMvelinqangi okunguyena okungokwakhe konke okusemazulwini nakho konke okusemhlabeni, ngempela ikuMvelinqangi lapho izindaba ziyoya khona ekugcineni"
  43,1,Ha Meem
  43,2,Ngencwadi ecacile
  43,3,Ngempela siyenze yaba iQur’an engesi-Arabhu ukuze niqonde
  43,4,Futhi ngempela yona ikumama wencwadi okuthina ophakeme onobuhlakani
  43,5,Ngakube sizosusa isikhumbuzo kunina ngoba ningabantu abamoshayo
  43,6,Futhi bangaki abaphrofethi esabathumela emandulo
  43,7,Futhi kwakungakaze kufike kubona umphrofethi ngaphandle kokuthi babemenza inhlekisa
  43,8,Ngakho-ke sababhubhisa labo ababeqatha kunabo ngamandla futhi sesadlula isibonelo sabasendulo
  43,9,"Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba ngempela bangathi, “owawadala ophakeme ngamandla owaziyo”"
  43,10,Okunguyena owanenzela umhlaba waba yindawo yokuphumula futhi wanenzela kuwona izindlela ukuze niholeke
  43,11,"Futhi okunguyena owehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni ngesilinganiso wayesevusa ngawo izwe elifile, niyovuswa kanjalo"
  43,12,Futhi okunguyena owadala zonke izinto ngambili futhi wanenzela imikhumbi kanye nezinkomo lezo enizigibelayo
  43,13,"Ukuze nigibele emihlane yazo bese nikhumbula umusa weNkosi yenu uma senigibele phezulu kwazo bese nithi, “udumo malube kulowo osenzele lokhu futhi thina besingeke sibenako”"
  43,14,Futhi ngempela eNkosini yethu siyophindela
  43,15,"Futhi bambekela ingxenye ezincekwini zakhe, ngempela umuntu akabongi ngokucacile"
  43,16,Noma ngakube wazithathela kulokho akudalayo amadodakazi wayesenikhethela amadodana na
  43,17,"Futhi uma oyedwa wabo etshelwa ngezindaba zalokho akwenzile okuyisibonelo konomusa, ubuso bakhe bubamnyama futhi agcwale usizi"
  43,18,Lowo okhuliswe ngemihlobiso kulapho yena esempikiswaneni engacacile
  43,19,"Futhi benza izingelosi isifazane lezo okuyizona eziyizinceku zonomusa, ngakube bakubona ukudalwa kwazo na"
  43,20,"Futhi bathi, “ukube wayethanda onomusa sasingeke sibakhonze”, abanalo ulwazi lwaloko (abenzi) lutho ngaphandle kokuqamba amanga"
  43,21,Noma sabanikeza incwadi ngaphambilini kwayo bona ababambelele kuyona
  43,22,"Kepha bathi, “ngempela thina safumana obaba bethu besendleleni futhi ngempela thina siholeleka ezinyathelweni zabo”"
  43,23,"Futhi kanjalo asizange ngaphambilini kwakho sithumele edolobheni (ebantwini) umxwayisi ngaphandle kokuthi abanothile balo bathi, “ngempela thina safumana obaba bethu besendleleni futhi ngempela nathi silandela ezinyathelweni zabo”"
  43,24,"Wathi “yize noma nginilethele ukuholwa okungcono kunalokho enabafumana kukona obaba benu? Bathi, “ngempela thina asikholelwa kulokho othunywe nako”"
  43,25,"Ngakho-ke saziphindisela kubona, bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho sabaphikayo"
  43,26,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi u-Abrahamu ethi kuyise nakubantu bakubo, “Angihlangene nalokho enikukhonzayo"
  43,27,Ngaphandle kwalowo owangidala futhi ngempela uzongihola
  43,28,Futhi wakwenza kwaba yigama eliseleyo ezizukulwaneni ukuze ziphenduke
  43,29,"Kepha, ngabanika injabulo laba kanye naboyise kwaze kwaba yilapho befikelwa yiqiniso kanye nesithunywa esicacile"
  43,30,"Futhi kwathi lapho sebefikelwa yiqiniso bathi, “leli yilumbo futhi ngempela thina asikholelwa kulona”"
  43,31,"Futhi bathi, “kungani ingembulwanga leQur’an emadodeni amakhulu amadolobha amakhulu"
  43,32,"Ngakube bona bayawuhlukanisa umusa weNkosi yakho, yithina esehlukanisayo phakathi kwabo ekuphileni kwabo empilweni yakulomhlaba futhi sabaphakamisa abanye babo ngaphezulu kwabanye ngamazinga ukuze abanye babo basebenzele abanye futhi umusa weNkosi yakho ungcono kunalokho abakuqoqela ndawonye"
  43,33,"Futhi ukube abantu babengesisona isizwe esisodwa, ngempela sasizobenzela labo abangakholwa konomusa uphahla lwesiliva ezindlini zabo kanye nezitebhisi abanyuka ngazo"
  43,34,Futhi okwezindlu zabo yiminyango kanye nemibhede abaphumula phezulu kwayo
  43,35,"Nomhlobiso wegolide, futhi konke lokho kuyinjabulo yempilo yalomhlaba futhi impilo ezayo eNkosini yakho ngeyabagwema okubi"
  43,36,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ofulathela isikhumbuzo sonomusa simvulela usathane ukuthi abe ngumngane wakhe
  43,37,Futhi ngempela bona (osathane) bayabavimbela endleleni futhi bacabanga ukuthi bona bangabaholiwe
  43,38,"Kuze kube yilapho efika kuthina athi, “ukube nje phakathi kwami nawe bekunebanga lezimpumalanga ezimbili, ububi umngane omubi"
  43,39,Futhi angeke kunisize namhlanje njengoba nenza okungenabo ubulungiswa ukuthi nina niyahlukaniselana esijezisweni
  43,40,Ngakube wena ungazenza yini izithuli ukuthi zizwe noma uhole izimpumputhe kanye noma ngabe ngubani osekudukeni okucacile
  43,41,"Noma ngabe siyakuthatha, ngempela thina siyoziphindisela kubona"
  43,42,"Noma sikukhombise lokho esabakhombisa kona, ngakho-ke ngempela sinamandla phezulu kwabo"
  43,43,"Ngakho-ke bambelela kulokho okwambuliwe kuwena, ngempela wena usendleleni eqondile"
  43,44,Futhi ngempela yona iyisikhumbuzo kuwena nakubantu bakho futhi niyobuzwa
  43,45,"Futhi buza noma ngabe ngobani esabathumela ngaphambilini kwakho abayizithunywa zethu, ngakube ngaphandle konomusa sibenzele yini izithixo ukuba bazikhonze"
  43,46,"Futhi ngempela samuthumela uMose namavesi ethu kuFaro kanye nakubabusi bakhe, ngakho-ke wathi, “ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa seNkosi yemihlaba”"
  43,47,Kepha kwathi lapho esefika kubona nezimpawu zethu kwaba yilapho bezihleka
  43,48,"Futhi asizange sibakhombise uphawu ngaphandle kokuba lubelukhulu kunolukanye nalo, futhi sabathatha ngesijeziso ukuze mhlawumbe babuye"
  43,49,"Futhi bathi, “Oh mlumbi! Sibizele iNkosi yakho ngalokho eyenza isethembiso ngako nawe, ngempela thina sizokuba ngabaholiwe”"
  43,50,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sesisisusile kubona isijeziso kwaba yilapho bona besephula (isethembiso)
  43,51,"Futhi uFaro wamemeza phakathi kwabantu bakhe wathi “O Bantu bami! Abusibona yini na obami ubukhosi base- Gibhithe? Kanye nalemifula egeleza ngaphansi kwami, ngakube aniboni yini"
  43,52,Ngakube angingcono yini kunalowo odelelekile (uMose) futhi akakwazi ukukhuluma ngokucacile
  43,53,Ngakho-ke kungani engabekwanga phezulu kwakhe amasongo egolide noma izingelosi zize kanye naye
  43,54,"Ngakho-ke uFaro wabakhohlisa abantu bakhe base beyamhlonipha, ngempela bona babengabantu abephula umthetho"
  43,55,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho besithukuthelisa saziphindisela kubona sabaminzisa bonke
  43,56,Futhi sabenza asebedlulile kanye nesibonelo kwabeza ngemumva
  43,57,FuthikwathilaphoindodanakaMariyayenziwanjengesibonelo kwaba yilapho abantu bakho bebanga umsindo ngayo (ngayo)
  43,58,"Futhi bathi, “ngakube onkulunkulu bethu abangcono noma uyena” abakwenzi lokho njengesibonelo ngaphandle kwempikiswano, kepha bona bangabantu abathanda ukuxabana"
  43,59,Akayilutho ngaphandle kokuba yinceku esabeka umusa phezulu kwayo futhi samenza wabayisibonelo ebantwini bakwa-Israyeli
  43,60,Futhi ukube sasithanda sasizokwenza izingelosi phakathi kwenu emhlabeni zibe ngezilandelayo
  43,61,"Futhi ngempela yena uwuphawu lwehora ngakho-ke ungangabazi ngalo futhi landelani mina, lena yindlela eqondile"
  43,62,"Futhi usathane anganivimbeli, ngempela yena uyisitha senu esigqamile"
  43,63,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi uJesu efika namavesi acacile wathi, “ngize kunina nobuhlakani nokuthi nginicacisele okunye kwalokho eniphikisana kukona ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe"
  43,64,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi yena uyiNkosi yami neNkosi yenu ngakho-ke mkhonzeni, lena yindlela eqondile"
  43,65,"Kepha amaqembu phakathi kwabo ayephikisana, Oh usizi! Kulabo ababenza okungenabo ubulungiswa, esijezisweni sosuku lokugcina"
  43,66,Ngakube balindele ngaphandle kwehora ukuthi lifike kubona masinyane kulapho bona bengaboni
  43,67,Abangane ngalolosuku abanye babo bayokuba yizitha zabanye ngaphandle kwabagwema ukubi
  43,68,Oh zinceku zami! Alukho uvalo kunina namhlanje futhi nina angeke nibe wusizi
  43,69,Labo abakholwayo emavesini ethu futhi abazithoba ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi
  43,70,Ngenani esivandeni nina namakhosikazi enu nithokoze
  43,71,Kuzungeleziswe kubona izingqoko (amathileyi) egolide nezinkomishi futhi phakathi kuzona kunalokho okufiswa yimiphefumulo nokuthokozisa amehlo futhi nina lapho phakathi niyohlala ingunaphakade
  43,72,Lesi yisivande enenziwe ukuthi nisidle njengefa ngenxa yalokho enanikwenza
  43,73,Okwethu lapho phakathi yizithelo eziningi enidla kuzona
  43,74,Ngempela izoni zisesijezisweni sesihogo ingunaphakade
  43,75,Angeke bancishiselwe sona (isijeziso) futhi bona lapho phakathi bayophelelwa yithemba
  43,76,"Futhi asizange senze okungenabo ubulungiswa kubona kepha, bona babengabenzi bokungenabo ubulungiswa"
  43,77,"Futhi bayokhala, “Oh malik! yenza ukuthi iNkosi yakho isiqedele (isibulale) lokhu uyothi (umalik) ngempela nina nizohlala (lapha)"
  43,78,Ngempela sinifikele neqiniso kepha iningi lenu liyalizonda iqiniso
  43,79,Noma ngakube balenzile yini icebo odabeni? Kepha yithina abenzi bamacebo
  43,80,"Noma bacabanga ukuthi asizizwa yini izimfihlo zabo nezingxoxo zabo zangasese, yebo! Futhi izithunywa zethu zikanye nabo ziyabhala"
  43,81,Ithi uma kungukuthi onomusa unendodana ngakho-ke ngingowokuqala wezikhonzi
  43,82,"Mayidunyiswe iNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba iNkosi yesihlalo sobukhosi, ngaphezulu kwalokho abakuchazayo"
  43,83,Ngakho-ke bayeke bakhulume futhi badlale kuze kube bayahlangana ngosuku lwabo lolo abathenjiswa lona
  43,84,Futhi yena uyilowo Mvelinqangi emazulwini futhi onguMvelinqangi emhlabeni futhi yena unobuhlakani uyisazi
  43,85,Futhi ugcwele izibusiso lowo okungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili futhi lukuyena ulwazi lwehora futhi niyobuyiselwa kuyena
  43,86,Futhi labo abababizayo esikhundleni sakhe abanako ukuncengela ngaphandle kwalabo abafakazela iqiniso futhi bona bazi
  43,87,"Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owabadala, ngempela bazothi “nguMvelinqangi” baphendukiselwa kanjani emumva"
  43,88,"Futhi ukusho kwakhe, Oh Nkosi yami! Ngempela laba ngabantu abangakholwa"
  43,89,"Ngakho suka kubo futhi uthi, \"Ukuthula.\" Kepha bazokwazi"
  44,1,Ha Meem
  44,2,Ngencwadi ecacile
  44,3,"Ngempela\tsayithumela\tphansi\tebusuku\tobubusisiwe, ngempela thina sasingabaxwayisi"
  44,4,"Kubona\t(ubusuku)\tkunqunywe\tzonke\tizindaba ezonobuhlakani"
  44,5,"Udaba oluvela kuthina, ngempela thina sasingabathumeli"
  44,6,"Umusa ovela eNkosini yakho, ngempela yona ingezwayo eyaziyo"
  44,7,INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ukube nina beniqinisekile
  44,8,"Akukho okunokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe (uMvelinqangi) uyaphilisa futhi uyabulala, iNkosi yenu neNkosi yobaba benu basendulo"
  44,9,"Kepha bona basekungabazeni, bayazidlalela nje"
  44,10,Ngakho-ke lindela usuku lapho isibhababhaka siyoletha intuthu egqamile
  44,11,"Imboza abantu, lesi yisijeziso esibuhlungu"
  44,12,"Nkosi\tyethu\tsisuse\tkuthina\tisijeziso,\tngempela singabakholwayo"
  44,13,Bangaba kanjani nesikhumbuzo kulapho sezafika kubona izithunywa ezicacile
  44,14,"Babe sebeyasifulathela (isithunywa) futhi bathi, “sifundisiwe futhi siyahlanya”"
  44,15,"Ngempela\tsiyasisusa\tisijeziso\tkancane\tngempela\tnina niyaphindela (ekoneni)"
  44,16,"Ngosuku lapho siyobashaya ngokushaya okukhulu, ngempela thina singabaziphindiselayo"
  44,17,"Futhi ngempela sabalinga ngaphambilini kwabo abantu baFaro, futhi safika kubona isithunywa esihloniphekile"
  44,18,"(UMose wathi), “zikhulule zize kimina izinceku zikaMvelinqangi, ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esihloniphekile kunina”"
  44,19,"Futhi ningaziphakamisi ngokuphambene noMvelinqangi, ngempela mina ngize kunina negunya elicacile"
  44,20,Futhi ngempela ngifune isiphephelo eNkosini yami neNkosi yenu hleze ningikhande ngamatshe
  44,21,"Kepha uma ningangikholwa, ngakho-ke qhelelanani nami"
  44,22,(UMose) wabe esebiza iNkosi yakhe ukuthi laba bangabantu abayizoni
  44,23,Ngakho-ke hamba nezinceku zami ebusuku ngempela nina nizolandelwa
  44,24,Futhi ushiye ulwandle lucwebile ngempela bona bayimpi ezominza
  44,25,Zingaki izivande nemithombo abayishiya ngemumva
  44,26,Kanye namasimu nezindawo ezinhle
  44,27,Nobuntofontofo (bempilo) ababethokoza kubona
  44,28,"Kanjalo\tsabenza\tabanye\tabantu\tbabayizindlalifa\tzawo (umhlaba)"
  44,29,Ngakho-ke izulu nomhlaba akuzange kubakhalele futhi abazange baphunyuzwe (abantu baFaro)
  44,30,"Futhi\tngempela\tsabasindisa\tabantwana\tbakwa-Israyeli esijezisweni esidumazayo"
  44,31,"KuFaro, ngempela yena wayephakeme phakathi kwabakhonza izithombe"
  44,32,Futhi ngempela sabakhetha ngolwazi ngaphezulu kwemihlaba
  44,33,Futhi sabanika ezimpawini okunokulingwa okucacile kuzona
  44,34,Ngempela laba bathi
  44,35,Akuyilutho lokho ngaphandle kokufa kwethu kokuqala futhi thina angeke sivuswe kwabafileyo
  44,36,Ngakho-ke lethani obaba bethu uma kungukuthi nina ningabaqinisileyo
  44,37,Ngakube bona bangcono noma abantu baseTubba kanye nalabo ababengaphambilini kwabo na? Sababhubhisa ngempela bona babeyizoni
  44,38,Futhi asizange siwadale amazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngokudlala
  44,39,Asizange sikudale kokubili (amazulu nomhlaba) ngaphandle kweqiniso kepha iningi labo alazi
  44,40,Ngempela usuku lokwahlulela yisikhathi esinqunyelwe bona bonke
  44,41,Usuku lapho umngane engeke amsize ngalutho umngane futhi bona angeke balekelelwe
  44,42,"Ngaphandle\tkwalabo\tuMvelinqangi\tanomusa\tkubona, ngempela yena ungophakeme ngamandla onesihawu"
  44,43,Ngempela isihlahla sezaqum
  44,44,Ukudla kwezoni
  44,45,"Njengamafutha abilayo, abila eziswini"
  44,46,Njengokugxabha kwamanzi abilayo
  44,47,Mthatheni bese nimdonsela maphakathi nesihogo
  44,48,Bese nithela phezulu kwekhanda lakhe isijeziso samanzi abilayo
  44,49,"Yizwa,\tngempela\twena\twawuphakeme\tngamandla uhloniphekile"
  44,50,Ngempela lokhu yilokho nina enanikungabaza
  44,51,Ngempela abalungileyo bayokuba sendaweni ephephile
  44,52,Ezivandeni nasemithonjeni
  44,53,Begqoke usilika nokuhlotshiswe ngokugqamile bebhekene
  44,54,Kanjalo siyobashadisa namakhosikazi amahle anamehlo amahle amakhulu
  44,55,"Lapho\tphakathi\tbayobiza\tzonke\t(izinhlobo)\tzezithelo ngokuthula bephephile"
  44,56,Lapho phakathi angeke bakuzwe ukufa ngaphandle kokufa kokuqala futhi uyobasindisa esijezisweni somlilo ovuthayo
  44,57,"Ngumusa ovela eNkosini yakho, lokho ukuphumelela okukhulu"
  44,58,"Ngempela\tsakwenza\tkwabalula\tolimini\tlwakho\tukuze bakhumbule"
  44,59,Ngakho-ke linda ngempela bona bangabalindileyo
  45,1,Ha Meem
  45,2,"Isambulo\rsencwadi\rsivela\rkuMvelinqangi\rophakeme\rngamandla onobuhlakani"
  45,3,Ngempela emazulwini nasemhlabeni kunezimpawu kwabakholwayo
  45,4,Futhi ekudalweni kwenu nakho konke nakusakazayo (emhlabeni) okuyizidalwa ezinyakazayo kuyizimpawu kubantu abaqinisekile (enkolweni)
  45,5,Futhi ukuphambana kobusuku nemini kanye nalokho okwehliselwaphansinguMvelinqangiokuvelaesibhakabhakeni okuyisabelo (imvula) bese ephilisa ngayo umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo nokushintsha kwemimoya kuyizimpawu kubantu abanomqondo
  45,6,Lawa ngamavesi kaMvelinqangi siwafundela wena ngeqiniso ngakho-ke iyiphi inkulumo abayokholwa yiyo emva kukaMvelinqangi nezimpawu namavesi akhe
  45,7,Usizi kulowo nalowo mqambimanga oyisoni
  45,8,"Owezwayo amavesi kaMvelinqangi efundelwa wona bese eqhubeka nokuziqhenya, kube sengathi akawezwa, ngakho-ke mtshene ngesijeziso esibuhlungu"
  45,9,Futhi uma esekufundile okuthize emavesini ethu ukuthatha njengenhlekisa labo-ke okwabo yisijeziso esijabhisayo
  45,10,Ngaphambili kwabo kunesihogo futhi angeke kubasize ngalutho lokho ababekusebenzela ngisho nalokho abakuthatha njengabavikeli esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi futhi okwabo yisijeziso esikhulu
  45,11,"Lokhu ukuholwa, futhi labo abangakholelwa emavesini eNkosi yabo okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu seRijz"
  45,12,NguMvelinqangi owanenzela ulwandle lwanithobela ukuze imikhumbi ihambe kulona ngempoqo yakhe futhi ukuze nifune ububele bakhe futhi ukuze nibonge
  45,13,"Futhi wanenzela yanithobela noma ngabe yini esemazulwini kanye nakho konke okusemhlabeni, kuvela kuyena, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kubantu abacabangayo"
  45,14,Ithi kulabo abakholwayo abathethelele labo abangazethembi izinsuku zikaMvelinqangi ukuze anike umvuzo abantu ngenxa yalokho ababekusebenzela
  45,15,Noma ngabe ngubani owenza izenzo ezinhle kungokwakhe uqobo futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza okubi ngakho-ke kuphambene naye bese nibuyiselwa eNkosini yenu
  45,16,Futhi ngempela sabanikeza abantwana bakwa-Israyeli incwadi nesehlulelo nobuphrofethi futhi sababela ezintweni ezinhle futhi sabakhetha ngaphezulu kwemihlaba
  45,17,"Futhi sabanikeza ubufakazi obucacile odabeni, ngakho-ke abazange baphikisane kwaze kwaba yingemumva kokuba sebefikelwe ulwazi ngenxa yomona phakathi kwabo, ngempela iNkosi yakho iyokwehlulela phakathi kwabo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo kulokho ababephikisana kukona"
  45,18,"Sabe sesikwenza ukuthi ube sendleleni esemthethweni empoqweni, ngakho-ke yilandele, ungalandeli izifiso zalabo abangazi"
  45,19,"Ngempela bona abasoze bakusize ngalutho maqondana noMvelinqangi futhi ngempela izoni ezinye zazo zingabangane zezinye, kepha uMvelinqangi ungumvikeli wabalungileyo"
  45,20,Lokhu kuwukubona okucacile kubantu nokuholeleka (endleleni elungileyo) kanye nomusa kubantu abaqinisekile (enkolweni)
  45,21,"Noma ngakube labo abenza izenzo ezimbi bacabanga ukuthi siyobenza njengalabo abakholwayo futhi abenze okuhle okulungileyo? Iyalingana impilo yabo kanye nokufa kwabo, okubi yilokho abakwehlulelayo"
  45,22,"Futhi uMvelinqangi wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeqiniso futhi ukuze anike umvuzo yonke imiphefumulo ngenxa yalokho eyakusebenzela, futhi bona angeke benziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa"
  45,23,"Ngakube umbonile yini lowo othathe njengonkulunkulu wakhe ukufisa kwakhe? Futhi uMvelinqangi umshiye ekudukeni ngenxa yolwazi futhi wasicilela ukuzwa kwakhe nenhliziyo yakhe futhi wabeka isembozo ekuboneni kwakhe, ngakho-ke ngubani ongamhola emva kukaMvelinqangi? Ngakube anikhumbuli yini na"
  45,24,"Futhi bathi, “akuyilutho ngaphandle kwempilo yethu yasemhlabeni, siyafa futhi siyaphila futhi akukho okungasibhubhisa ngaphandle kwesikhathi” futhi abanalo ulwazi ngalokho, kuphela bayazicabangela nje"
  45,25,"Futhi uma befundelwa amavesi ethu acacile, kuphela ukuphika kwabo ukuthi bathi, “lethani obaba bethu uma kungukuthi nina niqinisile”"
  45,26,"Yithi, “uMvelinqangi uyaniphilisa bese enenza ukuthi nife bese eniqoqela ndawonye ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo okungekho ukungabaza kulona, kepha iningi labantu alazi”"
  45,27,"Futhi ungokaMvelinqangi umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba futhi ngosuku lokufika kwehora, ngalolosuku bayolahlekelwa abalandeli bamanga"
  45,28,"Futhi uyozibona zonke izizwe ziguqe phansi, zonke izizwe ziyobizelwa kokubhalwe encwadini yazo, ngalolusuku nizonikwa umvuzo ngalokho enanikwenza"
  45,29,"Lena yincwadi yethu ekhuluma nani ngeqiniso, ngempela thina sasikubhala lokho enanikwenza"
  45,30,"Ngakho-ke labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okuhle okulungileyo iNkosi yabo iyobangenisa emseni wayo, lokho ukuphumelela okucacile"
  45,31,Kepha labo abangakholwanga ngakube akazange yini amavesi ami afundelwe nina? Nabe seniyazikhukhumeza futhi ningabantu abayizoni
  45,32,"Futhi uma kuthiwa ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso nehora akukho ukungabaza kulona nathi “asazi ukuthi yini ihora, sicabanga umcabango nje futhi thina asenelisekile (ngalo)"
  45,33,Futhi buyovela kubona ububi baloko ababekwenza futhi kuyobazungeleza lokho ababenza ngako inhlekisa
  45,34,"Futhi kuyothiwa, “ngalolusuku sizonikhohlwa njengoba nakhohlwa ukuhlangana ngalolusuku lwenu”"
  45,35,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi nina nanithatha amavesi kaMvelinqangi njengenhlekisa futhi yanikhohlisa impilo yalomhlaba ngakho-ke ngalolusuku angeke bakhishwe kusona (isihogo) futhi bona angeke bemukelwe emseni kaMvelinqangi
  45,36,Ngakho-ke udumo ngolukaMvelinqangi iNkosi yamazulu neNkosi yezwe iNkosi yemihlaba
  45,37,Futhi ngobakhe ubukhosi emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  46,1,Ha Meem
  46,2,Isambulo sencwadi sivela kuMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla onobuhlakani
  46,3,Asizange siwadale amazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngaphandle kweqiniso nesikhathi esinqunyiwe futhi labo abangakholwanga lokho abaxwayiswe ngako bayakufulathela
  46,4,"Ithi, “ngakube nikubonile yini lokho enikukhonzayo esikhundlenisikaMvelinqangi, ngikhombiseniukuthibadalani emhlabeni noma ngakube banayo yini ingxenye emazulwini? Ngiletheleni incwadi yangaphambilini kwalena noma insalela yolwazi uma kungukuthi nina ningabaqinisileyo”"
  46,5,Futhi ngubani oduke kakhulu kunalowo omemeza esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi labo abangamphenduli kuze kube wusuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo futhi bona bengakunakile ukubizwa kwabo
  46,6,Futhi ngenkathi abantu beqoqelwa ndawonye bayokuba yizitha kubona futhi bayokuphika ukubakhonza kwabo
  46,7,"Futhi ngenkathi befundelwa amavesi ethu acacile, labo abangazange bakholwe bathi, “ngeqiniso ngenkathi lifika kubona, lona ngumlingo ocacile”"
  46,8,"Nomabathi,“uyenzile(iQur’an)” ithi, “umangiyenzilengakho- ke angeke ningizuzele lutho kuMvelinqangi ungowaziyo kangcono ngalokho enikushoyo ngayo, wanele njengofakazi phakathi kwami nani futhi yena ungothethelelayo onomusa”"
  46,9,"Ithi, “angisiyena owokuqala ezithunyweni futhi angazi ukuthi kuyokwenziwani ngami nangani, angilandeli lutho ngaphandle kwalokho okwembulwe kumina futhi mina angiyilutho ngaphandle komxwayisi ogqamile”"
  46,10,"Ithi, “ngakube nibonile ukuthi uma ivela kuMvelinqangi nabe seniyayiphika (iQur’an) futhi wafakaza ufakazi ophuma phakathi kwabantwana bakwa-Israyeli (ngencwadi) efana nayo bese eyakholwa kulapho niqhosha, ngempela uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abayizoni”"
  46,11,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi kulabo abakholwayo ukube wawungcono umyalezo babengeke basidlule bawuthole kuqala kunathi futhi ngenkathi bengaholelekile ngawo bathi, “lawa ngamanga asemandulo”"
  46,12,"Futhi ngaphambilini kwayo kwakunencwadi kaMose, ukuhola nomusa futhi lena yincwadi eqinisekisa ngolimi lwesi-Arabhu ukuze ixwayise labo abenza okungenabo ubulungiswa"
  46,13,Ngempela labo abathi iNkosi yethu nguMvelinqangi bese bebambelela (kuloko) angeke kubekhona ukwesaba kubona futhi bona angeke baphatheke kabi
  46,14,Labo-ke bangabangane basezulwini bayohlala lapho phakathi ingunaphakade njengomvuzo ngenxa yalokho ababekwenza
  46,15,"Futhi samyala umuntu ngokwenza okuhle kubazali bakhe, unina wamkhulelwa kanzima futhi wamzala kanzima, futhi ukumkhulelwa kanye nokumlumula kwakhe (ukumsusa ebeleni) kuyizinyanga ezingamashumi amathathu kuze kube uyakhula afinyelele eminyakeni engamashumi amane athi, “ Nkosi yami ngenze ukuthi ngiwubonge umusa wakho lowo owubeke phezulu kwami kanye nakubazali bami nokuthi ngenze izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo ozithokozelayo futhi ungenzele ukulunga enzalweni yami, ngempela mina ngiphendukele kuwena ngokuzisola futhi ngempela mina ngingomunye wamaMuslim"
  46,16,"Labo-ke bayilabo esikwemukelayo kubona okuhle kakhulu lokho abakwenzayo futhi sizidlulise izenzo zabo ezimbi phakathi kwezihlali zezulu, isethembiso esiyiqiniso leso ababesethenjisiwe"
  46,17,"Futhi lowo othi kubazali bakhe, “uff kunina nobabili”, ngakube niyangethembisa ukuthi ngiyokhishwa (ngiyovuswa emhlabeni) kulapho sezadlula izizukulwane ngaphambilini kwami, futhi bona bobabili bacela usizo kuMvelinqangi, usizi kuwena! Kholwa ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso kepha uthi, “lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kwezinganekwane zasendulo”"
  46,18,"Labo-ke bayilabo elaqiniseka kubona igama, ezizukulwaneni esezadlula ngaphambilini kwabo zamajinn nabantu, ngempela bona babengabalahlekelwe"
  46,19,"Futhi kubona bonke kunamazinga (ahlukehlukene) ngokuhambelana nalokho ababekwenza, futhi ukuze abakhokhele ngezenzo zabo futhi bona angeke benziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa"
  46,20,"Futhi ngosuku lapho labo abangazange bakholwe belethwa emlilweni, “nina nazithola izinto zenu ezinhle empilweni yenu yalomhlaba nazithokozisa ngazo ngakho-ke ngalolusuku ninikwa umvuzo wesijeziso esijabhisayo ngenxa yokuthi nina naniziphakamisa emhlabeni ngokungesilona iqiniso nangenxa yokuthi nina nanephula umthetho"
  46,21,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi umfowabo ka’Ad exwayisa abantu bakhe emagqumeni ezihlabathi, futhi ngempela sebadlula abaxwayisi ngaphambilini kwakhe nangemumva kwakhe, ningakhonzi lutho ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi, ngempela mina nginesabela isijeziso sosuku olukhulu"
  46,22,"Bathi, “ngakube uze kuthina ukuze usididise konkulunkulu bethu na? Ngakho-ke silethele lokho osithembisa kona uma kungukuthi wena ungomunye wabaqinisile”"
  46,23,"Wathi, “kuphela ulwazi lukuMvelinqangi futhi nginitshena lokho engithunywe nako kepha mina nginibona ningabantu abangazi”"
  46,24,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebekubona njengefu elihlangene kusondela ngasezigodini zabo bathi, “leli yifu elisilethela imvula”, kepha kona kuyilokho enanikusheshisa, umoya ekunesijeziso esibuhlungu kuwona"
  46,25,"Ubhubhisa zonke izinto ngempoqo yeNkosi yawo, ngakho- ke kwangabonakali (lutho) ngaphandle kwezindawo zabo zokuhlala, sibanika kanjalo umvuzo abantu abayizoni"
  46,26,Futhi ngempela sabakha ngendlela esingazange sinakhe ngayo futhi sabenzela ukuzwa (amadlebe) nokubona (amehlo) nezinhliziyo kepha akuzange kubasize ngalutho ukuzwa kwabo nokubona kwabo nezinhliziyo zabo njengoba babephika amavesi kaMvelinqangi futhi kwabazungeleza lokho ababenza ngakho inhlekisa
  46,27,Futhi ngempela sakubhubhisa lokho okunizungelezile okungamadolobha futhi sawaphindaphinda amavesi ukuze babuye
  46,28,"Ngakho-ke kungani bengabasizanga labo ababebathatha esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi njengonkulunkulu ukuthi babasondeze, kepha banyamalala kubona, futhi lokho kungamanga nakho konke lokho ababekuqamba"
  46,29,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi sibhekisa kuwena idlanzana lamaJinn lilalela iQur’an, ngakho-ke kwathi lapho (amajinn) esefika kuyona athi, “lalelisani kahle” kwathi lapho seyiqediwe aphindela emumva kubantu bawo njengabaxwayisi"
  46,30,"(Amajinn) athi, “Oh Bantu bethu! Ngempela thina silalele incwadi eyembulwe ngemumva kukaMose igcwalisekisa leyo engaphambilini kwayo, iholela eqinisweni nasendleleni eqondile”"
  46,31,Oh Bantu bethu! Phendulani kummemi kaMvelinqangi futhi nikholelwe kuyena uzonithethelela izono zenu bese enisindisa esijezisweni esibuhlungu
  46,32,"Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongamphenduli ummemi kaMvelinqangi angeke aphunyuke emhlabeni futhi angeke abenabo abavikeli ngaphandle kwakhe, labo basekudukeni okucacile"
  46,33,"Ababoni yini ukuthi nguMvelinqangi lowo owadala amazulu nomhlaba futhi ayimsindi indalo yawo, uyakwazi ukuphilisa okufile, yebo! Ngempela yena uyakwazi ukwenza zonke izinto"
  46,34,"Futhi ngosuku lapho abangakholwanga beyolethwa emlilweni akusikona yini lokhu iqiniso? Bayothi, “yebo ngeNkosi yethu” athi, “ngakho-ke yizwani isijeziso ngenxa yokuthi anizange nikholwe”"
  46,35,Ngakho-ke yiba nesineke njengokuba izithunywa ezazizimisele zaba nesineke futhi ungafuni ukubasheshisela (ukubhubha kwabo) Ngosuku mzukwane bekubona lokho abethenjiswe kona (kuyokuba) sengathi abahlalanga (isikhathi) ngaphandle kwehora losuku. lokhu ukushumayela. Ngakho-ke abekho abayobhujiswa ngaphandle kwabantu abaphula umthetho
  47,1,Labo abangakholwanga futhi abavimba endleleni kaMvelinqangi uyoyenza ize leze imisebenzi yabo
  47,2,"Futhi labo abakholwayo abenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo futhi abakholelwa kulokho okwembulwa kuMuhammad futh kona kuyiqiniso elivela eNkosini yabo, iyozisusa kubona izenzo zabo ezimbi bese ilungisa isimo sabo"
  47,3,"Lokho kungenxa yokuthi labo abangakholwanga balandela okungesilona iqiniso kepha labo abakholwayo balandela iqiniso elivela eNkosini yabo, kanjalo uMvelinqangi wenzela abantu imifanekiso yabo"
  47,4,"Ngakho-keumanihlangana(empini) nalaboabangakholwanga bashayeni ezintanyeni zabo kuze kube yilapho nibehlula ngokugcwele, bese niqinisa ubudlelwane, emva kwalokho yisikhathi sesihe noma inhlengo kuze kube impi ibeka phansi umthwalo wayo, lokho ukube ubethanda uMvelinqangi wayezoziphindisela kubona, kepha ukuze avivinye abanye benu ngabanye, kepha labo ababulawa endleleni kaMvelinqangi ngakho-ke akasoze alahle imisebenzi yabo"
  47,5,Uyobahola futhi alungise isimo sabo
  47,6,Futhi abangenise ezulwini alazise bona
  47,7,Oh Nina enikholwayo! Uma nimelekelela uMvelinqangi uyonilekelela futhi asimamise izinyawo zenu
  47,8,Futhi labo abangakholwanga okwabo yimbubhiso futhi uMvelinqangi uyoyilahla imisebenzi yabo
  47,9,Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi bayakuzonda lokho uMvelinqangi akwembulayo ngakho-ke wazenza zaba yize leze izenzo zabo
  47,10,"Ngakube abazange yini bahambe emhlabeni ukuze babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho salabo ababengaphambilini kwabo, uMvelinqangi wababhubhisa nokufana nako (kulinde) kulabo abangakholwa"
  47,11,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi uMvelinqangi ungumvikeli walabo abakholwayo futhi abangakholwa abanaye umvikeli
  47,12,Ngempela uMvelinqangi ungenisa labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo ezivandeni ekugeleza ngaphansi kwazo amanzi kulapho labo abangazange bakholwe bezithokozisa futhi bedla ngendlela okudla ngayo izinkomo futhi umlilo yindawo yabo yokuhlala
  47,13,"Futhi mangaki amadolobha ayenamandla amakhulu ukwedlula idolobha lakho lelo elakuxosha, sababhubhisa abazange babenaye umelekeleli"
  47,14,"Ngakube lowo osebufakazini obucacile obuvela eNkosini yakhe uyefana yini nalowo owenziwele sasihle isenzo sakhe esimbi, futhi balandela izifiso zabo"
  47,15,"Incazelo yesivande leso esethenjiswa abalungileyo kusona phakathi kunemifula yamanzi angashintshi ubuwona kanye nemifula yobisi okungashintshi ukunambitheka kwayo kanye nemifula yewayini elimnandi kwabaliphuzayo kanye nemifula yoju olwenziwe kahle futhi okwabo lapho phakathi yizona zonke izinhlobonhlobo zezithelo nentethelelo evela eNkosini yabo, njengalabo abasemlilweni ingunaphakade futhi baphuziswe amanzi abilayo bese enquma amathumbu abo"
  47,16,"Futhi phakathi kwabo kunalabo abakulalelayo kuze kuthi lapho uma besuka kuwena bathi kulabo abaphiwa ulwazi, “yini leyo ayishilo” labo bayilabo uMvelinqagi asicilele izinhliziyo zabo futhi abalandela izifiso zabo"
  47,17,Futhi labo abaholeleke (endleleni eqondile) uyabenyusela ekuholweni futhi ubanika ukulunga kwabo
  47,18,"Ngakube balindile ngaphandle kwehora ukuthi lifike kubona masinyane na? Kepha sezafika izimpawu zalo, ngakho-ke kuyokubanjani kubona uma sebefikelwa yisikhumbuzo sabo na"
  47,19,Ngakho-ke yazi ukuthi ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi futhi cela intethelelo ngesono sakho nesabesilisa abakholwayo nabesifazane abakholwayo futhi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi ukuhamba kwenu nendawo yenu yokuphumula
  47,20,"Futhi bathi labo abakholwayo, “kungani singembulwanga isahluko” kepha uma sesambulwa isahluko esinqumayo ekukhuluma ngokulwa kusona"
  47,21,"Ukuhlonipha nenkulumo enhle uma udaba selunqunyiwe, ukube babeneqiniso kuMvelinqangi kwakuzokuba ngcono kubona"
  47,22,Ngakho-ke uma niphenduka nenza inkohlakalo emhlabeni futhi ninqamula ubuhlobo benu
  47,23,Labo-ke bayilabo abaqalekisile uMvelinqangi wabenza babayizithuli futhi wavala ukubona kwabo
  47,24,Ngakube abacabangi yini ngeQur’an noma ezinhliziyweni zabo kunezihluthulelo
  47,25,"Ngempela labo abaphendukela emumva, ngemva kokuba sekusobala kubona ukuholwa, usathane wabayenga futhi wabagcwalisela ithemba"
  47,26,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi bona bathi kulabo abazonda lokho akwembula uMvelinqangi “siyonihlonipha kwezinye izindaba” futhi uMvelinqangi uyazazi izimfihlo zabo
  47,27,Kepha kuyobanjani uma izingelosi zibenza ukuthi bafe zibashaya ebusweni babo nasemihlane yabo na
  47,28,"Lokho kungenxa yokuthi bona babelandela lokho okucasula uMvelinqangi futhi bezonda injabulo yakhe, ngakho-ke wenza zaba yize leze izenzo zabo"
  47,29,Noma labo abanokugula ezinhliziyweni zabo bacabanga ukuthi angeke uMvelinqangi ayiveze inzondo yabo
  47,30,"Futhi uma sithanda sasizokukhombisa bona ukuze ubazi ngezimpawu zabo, futhi ubazi ngephimbo enkulumweni (yabo) futhi uMvelinqangi uyazazi izenzo zenu"
  47,31,Futhi ngempela sizonilinga kuze kube yilapho sibazi abazabalazayo phakathi kwenu kanye nababekezelayo futhi sivivinye izindaba zenu
  47,32,"Ngempela labo abangakholwanga futhi bevimba endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi bephikisa isithunywa emva kokuba sekucacile kubona ukuholwa, ayisoze yamlimaza uMvelinqangi into futhi uyokwenza imisebenzi yabo ize leze"
  47,33,Oh Nina enakholwayo! Hloniphani uMvelinqangi futhi nihloniphe isithunywa futhi ningenzi imisebenzi yenu ize leze
  47,34,Ngempela labo abangakholwanga futhi bevimba endleleni kaMvelinqangi babesebeyafa kulapho bona bengakholwa ngakho-ke akasoze abathethelele uMvelinqangi
  47,35,"Ngakho-ke ungaphatheki kabi bese nimemezela ukuthula kulapho nina ningaphezulu, futhi uMvelinqangi ukanye nani futhi akasoze anephuce imisebenzi yenu"
  47,36,Kuphela impilo yalomhlaba ngumdlalo nesilibaziso futhi uma nikholwa futhi nesaba (uMvelinqangi) uyoninika imivuzo yenu futhi akayiceli ingcebo yenu
  47,37,"Uma enganicela kona enicindezela, benizoncishana futhi ubezoyiveza inzondo yenu (ukungathandi kwenu)"
  47,38,Nilapha nina niyilabo enimenyelwe ukuthi nisebenzise endleleni kaMvelinqangi ngakho-ke phakathi kwenu kunalabo abancishanayo futhi noma ngabe ngubani oncishanayo kuphela uncishanela umphefumulo wakhe futhi uMvelinqangi akaswele kepha nina 39. ningabaswele futhi uma niphendukela emumva uzoletha abanye abantu esikhundleni senu bese bengafani njengani
  48,1,Ngempela sakunika ukunqoba okucacile
  48,2,Ukuze uMvelinqangi akuthethelele lokho okwenzile okuyizono zakho zangaphambilini nezangemumva futhi afeze ububele bakhe kuwena futhi akuholele endleleni elungile
  48,3,Futhi akusize uMvelinqangi ngosizo olukhulu
  48,4,Yena uyilowo owehlisela phansi ukuthula ezinhliziyweni zabakholwayo ukuze kunezeleleke ukholo kanye nokukholwa kwabo futhi angawaMvelinqangi amabutho amazulu nomhlaba futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uyazi unobuhlakani
  48,5,"Ukuze afake abesilisa abakholwayo nabesifazane abakholwayo ezivandeni ekugeleza ngaphansi kwazo amifula, bayohlala lapho phakathi ingunaphakade futhi asuse kubona ububi babo futhi lokho kuMvelinqangi kuyimpumelelo enkulu"
  48,6,"Futhi ajezise abazenzisi besilisa nabazenzisi besifazane kanye nabesilisa abakhonza izithombe nabesifazane abakhonza izithombe, abacabanga ngoMvelinqangi imicabango emibi phezulu kwabo kunokubi (isijeziso esibi) futhi wabathukuthelela uMvelinqangi futhi wabaqalekisa futhi wabalungiselela isihogo futhi kubi lapho kuyiwa khona"
  48,7,Futhi ngawaMvelinqangi amabutho amazulu nomhlaba futhi uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  48,8,Ngempela thina sakuthumela njengofakazi nomlethi wezindaba ezinhle nanjengomxwayisi
  48,9,UkuzenikholwekuMvelinqanginesithunywasakhenisilekelele futhi nisihloniphe futhi nimdumise (uMvelinqangi) ekuseni nantambama
  48,10,"Ngempela labo abakuthembisayo kuphela bathembisa uMvelinqangi, isandla sikaMvelinqangi singaphezulu kwezandla zabo, ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani owephula (isethembiso) kuphela usephulela ukulimala komphefumulo wakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani ogcwalisekisa lokho akuthembisa uMvelinqangi ngakho-ke uyomnika umvuzo omkhulu"
  48,11,"Bayothi kuwena labo abasalela ngemumva abayizihlali zasogwadule “ingcebo yethu kanye nemindeni yethu eyasilibazisa ngakho-ke sicelele intethelelo” basho ngezilimi zabo lokho okungekho ezinhliziyweni zabo ithi, “ngakho-ke ngubani onganizuzela kuMvelinqangi okuthize uma ehlose ukunilimaza noma uma ehlose ngani inzuzo kepha ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi lokho enikwenzayo ukunakile"
  48,12,Kepha nanicabanga ukuthi isithunywa kanye nabakholwayo abasoze baphindele emindenini yabo futhi kwenziwa kwabukeka kukuhle lokho ezinhliziyweni zenu futhi nacabanga umcabango omubi nabe seniba ngabantu abakhohlakele
  48,13,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongakholwa kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe ngakho-ke ngempela thina sabalungiselela abangakholwa (umlilo) ovuthayo
  48,14,"Futhi bungobukaMvelinqangi ubukhosi bamazulu nomhlaba, uthethelela lowo amthandayo futhi ajezise lowo amthandayo, futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo onesihawu"
  48,15,"Bayothi labo abasalela ngemumva uma seniphuma niya ezimpangweni zempi ukuyozithatha, “sivumeleni sinilandele” bafuna ukuguqula inkulumo kaMvelinqangi ithi, “anisoze nasilandela kanjalo uMvelinqangi washo ngaphambilini” ngakho-ke bayothi, “qhabobo ninomona ngathi” kepha babengaqondi ngaphandle kokuncane"
  48,16,Ithi kwabasalela ngemumva abayizihlali zasogwadule “niyobizelwa abantu abanamandla amakhulu ukuyolwa nabo noma bazinikele ngakho-ke uma nihlonipha uMvelinqangi uyoninika umvuzo omuhle kepha uma nifulathela njengoba nanifulathela ngaphambilini uyonijezisa ngesijeziso esibuhlungu
  48,17,"Akukho ukusolwa noma (icala) empumputheni futhi alikho koxhugayo futhi alikho icala nakogulayo, futhi noma ngabe ngubani ohlonipha uMvelinqangi kanye nesithunywa sakhe uyomfaka ezivandeni ekugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula futhi noma ngabe ngubani ophendukela emumva uyomjezisa ngesijeziso esibuhlungu"
  48,18,Ngempela uMvelinqangi wawathokozela amakholwa ngenkathi ekuqinisekisa (ekuthembisa) ngaphansi kwesihlahla futhi wayekwazi lokho okusezinhliziyweni zawo ngakho-ke wayesehlisela phansi ukuthula phezulu kwawo futhi wawanika umvuzo wokunqoba okuseduze
  48,19,Futhi izimpango zempi abayozithatha ziningi futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  48,20,"WanethembisauMvelinqangiizimpangoeziningieniyozithatha wabe esenisheshisela lokhu, futhi wazibamba izandla zabantu kunina futhi ukuze kube wuphawu kwabakholwayo futhi iniholele endleleni eqondile"
  48,21,"Nokunye anikakabi nawo amandla okuba nako, ngempela uMvelinqangi ukusingethe (ukuzungelezile) lokho futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi wenza zonke izinto"
  48,22,Futhi ukube labo abangakholwa balwa nani ngempela babezophendula imihlane (yabo) bese bengamtholi umvikeli noma umlekeleli
  48,23,Indlela kaMvelinqangi okuyiyona eseyadlula ngaphambilini futhi awusoze wayithola inguquko endleleni kaMvelinqangi
  48,24,Futhi yena uyilowo owabamba izandla zabo kunina nezandla zenu kubona maphakathi neMakkah emva kokuba enenze naba abanqobi kubona futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyakubona lokho enikwenzayo
  48,25,"Bona bayilabo abangakholwa futhi abanivimbelayo eMasjid al-Haraam bavimbela umnikelo ukuthi ufike endaweni yabo, futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yamadoda akholwayo nabesifazane abakholwayo enaningabazi eningase nibanyathele obekuzonehlela ngabo ukusolwa ngaphandle kolwazi, ukuze uMvelinqangi angenise emseni wakhe lowo amthandayo, ukube babehlukene ngempela sasizobajezisa labo abangakholwanga phakathi kwabo ngesijeziso esibuhlungu"
  48,26,"Ngenkathi labo abangakholwanga befaka ezinhliziyweni zabo intshisekelo, intshisekelo yokungazi ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi wehlisela phansi ukuthula kwakhe phezulu kwesithunywa sakhe kanye naphezulu kwabakholwayo futhi wabanqumela igama lobumnene futhi babefanelwe yikona futhi bevumelekile kukona, futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyisazi sazo zonke zinto"
  48,27,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi wasikhombisa isithunywa umbono weqiniso ukuthi ngempela nizongena emasjid al-Haraam, uma uMvelinqangi ethanda, niphephile nigundile emakhanda enu futhi niziphungulile (izinwele zenu) ningesabi ngakho- ke uyakwazi lokho eningakwazi wayesebeka ngaphandle kwalokho ukunqoba okuseduze"
  48,28,Yena (uMvelinqangi) uyilowo owathumela isithunywa sakhe nokuhola nenkolo eyiqiniso ukuze ayenze igqame ngaphezulu kwazo zonke izinkolo futhi wanele uMvelinqangi njengofakazi
  48,29,"UMuhammad yisithunywa sikaMvelinqangi futhi labo abakanye naye banzima kwabangakholwa, banomusa phakathi kwabo, ubabona bekhothama beguqa befuna umusa ovela kuMvelinqangi nentokozo izimpawu zabo zisebusweni babo ngenxa yokuguqa bewa ngeziphongo lokho kuwukuchazwa kwabo kwiTorah nokuchazwa kwabo kwi-Injil (ivangeli) njengesithombo esiveza okumilayo kwaso bese siyakuqinisa kube kukhulu bese kuyama ngesiqu sako kusimame kuthokozise abatshali ukuze abathukuthelise abangakholwayo, uMvelinqangi wabathembisa labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okuhle okulungileyo phakathi kwabo intethelelo nomvuzo omkhulu"
  49,1,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ningenzi (okuthize) ngaphambili kukaMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyezwa uyazi"
  49,2,Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ningaphakamisi amazwi enu ngaphezulu kwezwi likamphrofethi futhi ningabi nomsindo kuyena ngenkulumo njengokuba nomsindo kwabanye benu kwabanye hleze izenzo zenu zibe yize leze kulapho nina ningaboni
  49,3,Ngempela labo abehlisa amazwi abo uma kukhona isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi labo-ke bayilabo uMvelinqangi azivivinyela okulungileyo izinhliziyo zabo okwabo yintethelelo kanye nomvuzo omkhulu
  49,4,Ngempela labo abakubiza ngemumva kwezindawo zokuhlala iningi labo alinawo umqondo
  49,5,"Futhi ukube bona babebekezela kuze kube uyaphuma uya kubona kwakuzokuba ngcono kubona, futhi uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo onesihawu"
  49,6,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Uma (umuntu) ongalungile efika kunina nezindaba ngakho-ke zihlolisiseni, hleze nilimaze abantu ngokungazi bese niyazisola ngalokho enanikwenza"
  49,7,Futhi yazini ukuthi phakathi kwenu kukhona isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi ukube besinganilalela ezindabeni eziningi ngempela benizokuba senhluphekweni kepha uMvelinqangi wayenza yathandeka kunina inkolo futhi wayenza yabukeka iyinhle ezinhliziyweni zenu futhi wenza kwazondeka kunina ukungakholwa nokushinga nokungahloniphi labo-ke bayilabo abaholwe kahle
  49,8,Umusa ovela kuMvelinqangi kanye nobubele futhi uMvelinqangi uyisazi unobuhlakani
  49,9,"Futhi uma amaqembu amabili amakholwa elwa ngakho- ke yenzani ubulungiswa phakathi kwawo womabili kepha uma elilodwa lawo womabili licindezela elinye ngakho-ke yilwani nalelo elicindezelayo kuze kube lithobela impoqo kaMvelinqangi, kepha uma lizithoba ngakho-ke lamulani phakathi kwawo womabili ngobulungiswa nangokulingana, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyabathanda abalinganisayo"
  49,10,Abakholwayo bangabazalwane ngakho-ke lamula phakathi kwabafowenu futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi ukuze ninikwe umusa
  49,11,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Abantu abangabenzi abantu iziphukuphuku, bangaba ngcono kunabo, futhi abesifazane bangabenzi (iziphukuphuku abanye) besifazane, mhlawumbe bangaba ngcono kunabo futhi ningathukani, futhi ningabizani ngezigcono (ezithukuthelisayo) yigama elibi lokungahloniphi emva kwenkolo, futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongazisoli – ngakho-ke labo bona bangabenzi bokubi"
  49,12,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Qhelelanani kakhulu nomdlinzo ngempela eminye yemidlinzo iyisono futhi abanye benu bangabelusi abanye futhi bangabahlebi, ngakube oyedwa wenu uyakuthanda yini ukuthi adle inyama kamfowabo ofile? Ningayinyanya futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi ungowamukela ukuzisola unesihawu"
  49,13,"Oh Bantu! Ngempela thina sanidala ngesilisa nesifazane futhi sanenza abantu nezizwe ukuze nazane, ngempela ohlonipheke kakhulu phakathi kwenu kuMvelinqangi yilowo olunge kakhulu kunani, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyisazi welumkile"
  49,14,"Abahlali basogwadule bathi, “sasikholwa” ithi, “anikholwa” kepha yithini, “sizinikele” inkolo ayikangeni ezinhliziyweni zenu kepha uma nihlonipha uMvelinqangi kanye nesithunywa sakhe angeke anciphise lutho emisebenzini yenu, ngempela uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo onesihawu"
  49,15,"nesithunywa sakhe bese bengangabazi futhi bazabalaze ngengcebo yabo nangemiphefumulo yabo endleleni kaMvelinqangi, labo-ke bayilabo abaneqiniso"
  49,16,"Ithi ngakube nazisa uMvelinqangi ngenkolo yenu na? Kulapho uMvelinqangi ekwazi lokho okusemazulwini kanye nalokho okusemhlabeni, futhi uMvelinqangi uyisazi sazo zonke izinto"
  49,17,"Benza sengathi bakwenzela umusa ukuthi babengamaMuslim ithi, “ningenzi ububele kumina ngobu-Islam benu, kepha nguMvelinqangi owenza ububele kunina ngokuthi waniholela enkolweni uma kungukuthi nina ningabaneqiniso"
  49,18,Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyakwazi okungabonwa kwamazulu nomhlaba futhi uMvelinqangi ungumboni walokho enikwenzayo